-05-27 15:42:32',1),(79,'BUTTON_LOGIN_REGISTER','US','Sign in | Register','2008-02-04 17:05:41',1),(80,'BUTTON_LOGIN_REGISTER','DE','Login | Registrieren','2008-06-09 13:05:14',1),(102,'HOME_INTRO','US','Xara Xtreme is quite simply the world\'s fastest graphics software, with truly&nbsp;flexible illustration tools and revolutionary photo handling.&nbsp;A single application for all types of creative work, whether it\'s vector drawings, DTP, photo composition, Website design or Flash animation. Comes in Pro and Classic versions.','2009-10-14 19:34:52',1),(2229,'BUTTON_BUYNOW','US','BUY NOW','2008-05-08 15:32:29',1),(447,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_SHORT','DE','Die Werkzeuge von Xara Xtreme ermöglichen es Ihnen Effekte wie Transparenz, Schatten, Kanten oder Füllverläufe auf interaktive, schnelle und intuitive Weise zu erstellen. Keine störenden Dialoge - Ziehen Sie die Effekte einfach auf die Objekte!','2008-06-13 15:38:46',1),(1781,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_LONG','DE','<p>Konturen um ein Objekt zu legen ist mit dem Xara Xtreme <strong>Kontur-Werkzeug</strong> möglich. Konturen sind ein <strong>Spezialeffekt</strong>, der <strong>gleichmäßig große konzentrische Ringe</strong> innen oder außen um ein Objekt legt. Diese Ringe können in den Hintergrund <strong>überblenden </strong>oder über einen <strong>Farbregenbogen </strong>verlaufen. </p>\r\n<p>Sobald Sie eine Kontur auf ein Objekt gelegt haben, ändert diese sich mit dem Objekt, wenn Sie dieses <strong>vergrößern </strong>oder anderweitig <strong>verändern</strong>. Sie können die Kontur selbst <strong>bearbeiten </strong>und Ihre Eigenschaften, inklusive des Abstandes zwischen den Schritten, die Anzahl der Schritte, die Konturbreite und Ihr Profil, verändern.</p>\r\n<p>Die Schaltfläche <strong>„Eingelassener Pfad“</strong> <strong>konvertiert </strong>Ihr Objekt mit Kontur in eine größere oder kleinere Form und entfernt die Kontur. Dies gibt Ihnen größere Flexibilität als nur das Objekt neu zu skalieren, da es die <strong>Dicke </strong>ändert im Gegensatz zur Größe.</p>','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(1782,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(445,'FEATURE_TEXT_H-LING_SHORT','DE','Mit dem Text-Werkzeug können Sie Text in Zeilen, Spalten oder sogar quer über mehrere Seiten verlaufen lassen. Sie erhalten volle Kontrolle über das Formatieren des Textes. Dadurch wird Xara Xtreme zum idealen Werkzeug für DTP-Projekte wie Broschüren und Newsletter, die Zeichnungen, Fotos und Text miteinander vereinen.','2008-06-04 15:02:28',1),(1780,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_SHORT','DE','Konturen um ein Objekt zu legen ist mit dem Xara Xtreme Kontur-Werkzeug möglich. Konturen sind ein Spezialeffekt, der gleichmäßig große konzentrische Ringe innen oder außen um ein Objekt legt. Diese Ringe können in den Hintergrund überblenden oder über einen Farbregenbogen verlaufen. ','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(446,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_NAME','DE','Direct Action Tools','2008-06-13 15:38:46',1),(443,'FEATURE_PSD_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_LONG','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1774,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_LONG','DE','<p>Das Xara Xtreme <strong>Überblendungs-Werkzeug</strong> erlaubt es Ihnen, zwischen zwei Objekten zu überblenden oder diese zu vereinen. Diese Objekte können alle verfügbaren Objekttypen sein (Text, Bitmaps, Formen) oder sogar andere Überblendungen.</p>\r\n<p>Mit dem Werkzeug erzeugen Sie eine <strong>Reihe von Zwischenobjekten</strong>, so dass ein <strong>Übergang </strong>vom Anfangsobjekt zum Endobjekt entsteht. Sie können die Anzahl der Überblendungsschritte einstellen und auch mehr als einen Zwischenpunkt haben, so dass Sie zwischen mehreren Objekten blenden können.</p>\r\n<p>Überblendungen können dazu verwendet werden, <strong>komplete Schlaglichter</strong>, <strong>verschwommene Kanten</strong> an Objekten, <strong>sich wiederholende Muster</strong> und viele andere Effekte zu erstellen. Sie können sogar <strong>Objekte </strong>innerhalb der Überblendung, nachdem Sie sie geschaffen haben, <strong>editieren</strong>. Sie können auch Überblendungen an <strong>einem bestimmten Weg</strong> entlanglaufen lassen, wie z. B. einer Kurve.</p>\r\n<p>Zur Feinabstimmung haben Überblendungen auch eine <strong><a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=20\">Profilkontrolle</a></strong>, in der Sie die Veränderungsrate der Schritte und andere Attribute einstellen können.</p>\r\n<p>Das Überblenden in Xara Xtreme ist sehr schnell und Speicher-sparend im Vergleich zu anderen Zeichen-Programmen - das bedeutet, dass Sie weniger warten müssen und weniger Systemressourcen benötigt werden.&nbsp;</p>','2008-09-03 16:30:19',1),(1775,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1776,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_NAME','DE','Weiche Vektoren','2008-06-05 15:19:19',1),(1777,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_SHORT','DE','Xara war die erste Anwendung, die Randunschärfe und weiche Schatten für Vektoren bot. Seine Technik ist immer noch am weitesten entwickelt und ermöglicht hochqualitative realistische Bilder, die schneller und einfacher als mit jeder anderen Software erschaffen werden können.\r\nRandunschärfe, zusammen mit Transparenz, gibt sowohl großartige Foto-Kompositions-Möglichkeiten als auch sehr gute Vektoren-Schattierung.','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(1778,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_LONG','DE','<p>Randunschärfe macht die <strong>Kanten </strong>von Objekten leicht <strong>unscharf</strong>, so dass diese in den Hintergrund überblenden - bisher unmöglich für Vektor-Zeichenprogramme.</p>\r\n<p>Sie wählen einfach ein Objekt - <strong>jedes Objekt</strong> inkl. Formen, Text, Fotos und sogar ClipAnsichten -&nbsp; und bewegen den Schieberegler für Randunschäfte. Das ausgewählte Objekt <strong>vereinigt </strong>sich langsam mit den Hintergrundobjekten, wodurch eine <strong>scharfe Linie</strong> am Rand vermieden wird. Vor allem wenn man Objekte auf Bitmaps legt, ist das sinnvoll. </p>\r\n<p>Sie können in Xara Xtreme das <strong><a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=20\">Profil</a></strong> für Randunschärfe ändern, den Übergang am Rand also anpassen. Sie möchten vielleicht eine normale Übergangsrate, die Veränderung stärker an ein Ende verschoben oder in der Mitte.</p>\r\n<p>Beachten Sie, dass Randunschärfe <strong>nur </strong>die Kanten von Objekten betrifft und keinen Einfluss auf andere Teile des Objektes hat.</p>eme ist sehr schnell und Speicher-sparend im Vergleich zu anderen Zeichen-Programmen - das bedeutet, dass Sie weniger warten müssen und weniger Systemressourcen benötigt werden.&nbsp;','2008-09-03 16:33:44',1),(1779,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(441,'FEATURE_PSD_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_NAME','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(442,'FEATURE_PSD_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_SHORT','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1773,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_SHORT','DE','Das Überblendungs-Werkzeug tweent oder blendet von einer Form in eine andere. Dabei ist es sehr schnell: Einfach klicken und ziehen! Es funktioniert mit Vektor-Formen, Text und Fotos.','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(448,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_LONG','DE','<p>Mti den <strong>Direct Action Tools</strong> von Xara Xtreme können Sie Effekte wie Transparenz, Kanten oder abgestufte Füllungen kreieren indem Sie das jeweilige Werkzeug auswählen und dann über die entsprechende Grafik ziehen. So kann man z. B. ein Werkzeug über ein Objekt ziehen, um einen Farbverlauf (im Füllwerkzeug) oder eine Transparenz (im Transparenzwerkzeug)&nbsp; zu erstellen. Alternativ kann man auch am Objekt zum Positionieren eines Schatten (Schattenwerkzeug) oder&nbsp; zum Drehen in 3D (Extrudier-Werkzeug) ziehen.</p>\r\n<p>Traditionsgemäß würde man für diese Effekte die Werte in ein <strong>Dialogfenster </strong>eingeben, von wo aus sie auf die Grafik übertragen werden. Mit den Direct Action Tools von Xara Xtreme können alle Effekte auf das Objekt selbst angewendet werden, ohne die Zahlen zuerst in einen Dialog eingeben zu müssen. Die Änderungen sind sofort sichtbar – <strong>Sie bekommen das Gefühl, als würden Sie Ihre Hände direkt einsetzen</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Hierdurch bietet sich ein gewaltiger Vorteil: die Kreativität Ihrer Arbeit und das Bild selber bleiben im Mittelpunkt – und Sie sparen viel Zeit! Auch das <strong>Experimentieren </strong>mit Effekten wird viel einfacher. </p>\r\n<p>Die Direct Action Tools umfassen die Werkzeuge für <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=48\">Kanten,</a> <a  href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=50\">Schatten</a>, <a  href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=44\">Transparenz</a>, Füllungen, <a  href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=47\">Konturen</a>,&nbsp;<a  href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=82\">3D-Extrusion</a> und <a  href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=45\">Blenden</a>.</p>','2008-06-13 15:52:02',1),(1684,'FEATURE_PRINTING_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1763,'FEATURE_DRAG_-_DROP_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1764,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_SHORT','DE','Anstatt nur die Umrisse zu zeigen, wenn Sie ein Objekt verschieben, rotieren oder seine Größe ändern, zeigt Xtreme Ihnen direkt die Veränderung am gesamten Objekt. Nur Xtreme kann dies bei komplexen Vektor-Grafiken.','2008-06-13 16:25:22',1),(1765,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_LONG','DE','Xara Xtreme ist eines der ersten Programme der Welt, in denen Sie live Ihre Objekte als Ganzes verschieben, skalieren oder drehen können, um direkt einen Eindruck vom Endprodukt zu bekommen. Das heißt, sobald Sie die Position oder Größe ändern oder Ihr Objekt drehen, bewegt sich das gesamte Objekt und nicht nur ein Umriss. So ist es viel einfacher, zu beurteilen, welchen Effekt die Bearbeitung haben wird.','2008-06-05 13:51:36',1),(1766,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_SHORT','DE','Es ist sehr wichtig für ein Grafik-Paket, dass man Dinge, die man gemacht hat, auch wieder rückgängig machen kann. Xara Xtreme erlaubt Ihnen unendlich viele Rückgängig-Schritte, so dass Experimentieren leicht gemacht ist.','2008-06-05 13:55:27',1),(1767,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_LONG','DE','<p>Es ist sehr wichtig für ein Grafik-Paket, dass man Bearbeitungen, die man gemacht hat, auch wieder ändern kann. Mit Xara Xtreme können Sie einfach Ihre letzten Veränderungen an einem Dokument <strong>rückgängig machen</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Mit der Taste „Rückgängig“ werden Sie alle Veränderungen, die Sie <strong>aus Versehen</strong> gemacht haben, wieder los. Die, die <strong>schiefgegangen</strong> sind ebenso, wie solche, die sie einfach <strong>nicht mögen</strong>. „Rückgängig“ is eine starke Option wenn man sie mit „Wiederherstellen“ kombiniert. Sie haben dann die <strong>Freiheit </strong>mit einer Zeichnung herum zu <strong>experimentieren </strong>mit dem sicheren Wissen, dass Sie alle Veränderungen rückgängig machen können. Sollten Sie sich dann entscheiden, dass Sie die Veränderung doch wollten, können Sie sie wiederherstellen.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Einige Grafik-Pakete haben nur eine <strong>begrenzte </strong>Anzahl an Rückgängig-Schritten, aber bei Xara Xtreme haben Sie <strong>keine Beschränkungen</strong>. So kann es sich alles merken, was Sie gemacht haben.</p>','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(1768,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1769,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_SHORT','DE','Xara war die erste Vektor-Anwendung, die Transparenzen eingeführt hat und bietet bis heute die einfachste, ausgefeilteste Transparenz-Kontrolle. Mit wenigen Klicks können Sie abgestufte Übergänge zu jedem Objekt, Foto, Text oder Vextor-Form erstellen.','2008-06-05 14:11:56',1),(1770,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_LONG','DE','<p>Jedes erstellte Objekt (inkl. Text und Bitmaps) kann, mithilfe der <strong>zahlreichen Transparenzoptionen</strong>, transparent gemacht werden.</p>\r\n<p>Wie beim Echtzeit Anti-Alias, war auch bei der<strong> Vektor-Transparenz</strong> Xara Pionier. Transparenz kann auf unterschiedliche Arten angewendet werden - eine der gängigsten ist die Simulation von Glas. Sie kann aber auch benutzt werden um <strong>subtile Reflektionen und Schlaglichter</strong> zu erschaffen, die sonst sehr schwer zu kreieren wären.</p>\r\n<p>Oft werden auch Teile einer Zeichnung mit zusätzlichen transparenten Objekten belegt, die dann als <strong>Filter </strong>fungieren um z. B. die Farbe oder den Kontrast eines Bildes zu verändern. Xara Xtreme gibt Ihnen auch die Möglichkeit Bitmaps Ihrer Wahl auf Ihren <strong>Transparenzen als Texturen</strong> zu verwenden. Damit erzielen Sie einen Spezialeffekt auf jeder Grafik oder Auswahl von Grafiken.</p>\r\n<p>Sie können Transparenz in einem linearen <strong>Verlauf </strong>anwenden oder in einer Auswahl an Formen, wie Diamant oder Kegel. Damit erzielen Sie ungewöhnliche Effekte. Transparenz kann in <strong>jede Richtung</strong> verlaufen und ist <strong>farbunabhängig </strong>- wählen Sie einfach das Transparenz-Werkzeug und klicken und ziehen Sie auf dem Bild um die Transparenz anzuwenden, <strong>komplett interaktiv und direkt</strong>.</p>','2008-06-13 16:56:57',1),(1771,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1772,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_NAME','DE','Überblendungs-Werkzeug','2008-06-05 14:26:08',1),(435,'FEATURE_CAT_NEW','DE','Neu','2008-05-27 15:42:32',1),(179,'FEATURE_ZOOM_NAME','US','Zoom','2008-05-01 14:02:15',1),(129,'FEATURE_CAT_THE_WEB','US','Web Design','2009-05-22 12:32:16',1),(130,'FEATURE_CAT_GENERAL','US','General','2009-02-02 17:01:36',1),(131,'FEATURE_CAT_WEB','US','Web','2008-02-12 16:53:43',1),(132,'FEATURE_CAT_PHOTO','US','Photo','2008-02-12 16:53:39',1),(133,'FEATURE_CAT_ILLUSTRATION','US','Illustration','2008-02-12 16:53:40',1),(134,'FEATURE_CAT_XTREME','US','Xara Xtreme','2008-02-12 16:53:45',0),(135,'FEATURE_CAT_XTREMEPRO','US','Xara Xtreme Pro','2008-02-13 08:53:40',0),(136,'FEATURE_CAT_GENERAL','DE','Allgemein','2008-05-27 15:42:32',1),(138,'FEATURE_CAT_ILLUSTRATION','DE','Illustration','2008-05-27 15:42:32',1),(139,'FEATURE_CAT_PHOTO','DE','Foto','2008-05-27 15:42:32',1),(140,'FEATURE_CAT_WEB','DE','Internet','2008-05-27 15:42:32',1),(178,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_KEYWORDS','US','direct action;bevel;shadow;transparency;fill;contour;3d;blend','2008-03-21 17:17:37',0),(175,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_NAME','US','Direct Action Tools','2008-03-21 17:17:37',1),(176,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme\'s Direct Action Tools allow you to create effects such as transparency, shadows, bevels or gradient fills in an interactive, fast and intuitive way. No distracting dialogs - simply drag on the object!','2008-03-21 17:17:37',1),(177,'FEATURE_DIRECT_ACTION_TOOLS_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme\'s <strong>Direct Action Tools</strong> allow you to create effects such as transparency, bevels or gradient fills by selecting the tool then dragging over the image itself to affect the required change. For example you can drag across an object to apply a graduated color (in the fill tool) or transparency (in the transparency tool), or drag on a shadow to position it (in the shadow tool), or drag on an object to rotate it in 3D (in the 3D extrude tool).<br />\r\n<br />Traditionally, to apply these sort of effects you&nbsp;would need to enter values&nbsp;in a <strong>dialog box</strong> and they are transferred to the drawing. With Xara Xtreme\'s Direct Action Tools, you can apply all these effects <strong>on the object itself</strong> - without having to enter any numbers in a dialog box! And the changes take place instantly - it\'s <strong>as close to using your hands as you will get</strong> with a graphics package. <br />\r\n<br />This is a BIG advantage, because it not only <strong>saves time</strong>, but also keeps the creative work and the image itself at the center of your focus. It makes <strong>experimenting</strong> with effects and settings much easier too. <br />\r\n<br />Direct Action Tools include the <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=48\">Bevel,</a> <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=50\">Shadow</a>, <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=44\">Transparency</a>, <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=49\">Fill</a>, <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=47\">Contour</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=82\">3D Extrude</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=45\">Blend</a> tools.','2009-05-27 18:22:19',1),(158,'FEATURE_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_NAME','US','Import and Export','2009-05-22 14:01:22',1),(159,'FEATURE_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_SHORT','US','Xtreme offers support for a huge range of file formats, making it easy to exchange your work with other users and programs. This includes common bitmap types (eg GIF, JPEG, BMP, PNG, TIFF, PSD, and RAW photos) and key vector types (eg PDF and AI/EPS, and EMF/WMF). For text Xara Xtreme supports RTF (Rich Text Format) and for websites HTML and Flash. ','2009-05-22 14:01:22',1),(160,'FEATURE_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme is used by many different types of customer in a spectacular range of uses - for drawings, text and photos, for print and the web -&nbsp;so we understand how important it is to offer compatibility with other products and users.&nbsp;Xtreme offers support for a very large range of file formats, making it easy to exchange your work with other users and programs.<br>\r\n<br>Xara Xtreme&nbsp;<strong>supports all the common graphics formats</strong>, including <strong>bitmap types</strong> like GIF, JPEG, BMP, PNG, TIFF and <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=10\"><strong>PSD</strong></a>, and the import of photos as <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=38\">RAW</a> or the new <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=87\">Photo HD</a> (Xtreme Pro only). Plus it supports the key <strong>vector types</strong> like <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=17\"><strong>PDF</strong></a>&nbsp;and AI (Adobe Illustrator)/EPS, EMF (extended metafile) and WMF (Windows metafile),&nbsp;SVG (export only);early versions of CorelDRAW CDR and CMX and many others that are not so well known.\r\n<p>For <strong>text</strong> Xara Xtreme supports RTF (<strong>Rich Text Format</strong>).&nbsp; You can import and export text in RTF format so it includes style information such as font, font size, color, margins, special and foreign characters (Unicode supported).</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re working on the web, then Xara Xtreme&nbsp;also offers integration with Adobe\'s <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=59\">Dreamweaver</a></strong> and can export <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=89\"><strong>Flash</strong></a>, &nbsp;<a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=58\"><strong>Animated GIF</strong></a> and <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=84\"><strong>HTML</strong></a> pages. </p>\r\n<p>Plus there\'s clipboard compatibility with the common <strong>Microsoft</strong> applications such as Outlook and Word.</p>','2009-05-22 14:01:22',1),(167,'FEATURE_PSD_SUPPORT_NAME','US','PSD Support','2008-04-07 17:53:46',1),(168,'FEATURE_PSD_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has full support for importing and exporting Adobe Photoshop® PSD files including layer support.','2008-04-07 17:53:46',1),(161,'FEATURE_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_KEYWORDS','US','GIF;JPEG;BMP;PNG;TIFF;AI;PDF;RTF;Dreamweaver;Flash;Word;Outlook;PSD;WMF;EMF;SVG;CDR;CMX;import;export;','2009-05-22 14:01:22',0),(162,'FEATURE_COLOR_SEPARATION_SUPPORT_NAME','US','Color Separation Support','2008-04-07 17:54:24',1),(163,'FEATURE_COLOR_SEPARATION_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme Pro offers the ability to produce CMYK color separations. This includes on-screen preview of CMYK and spot color plates, PANTONE® color support, spot colors, on-screen printer gamut preview and a lot more.','2008-04-07 17:54:24',1),(164,'FEATURE_COLOR_SEPARATION_SUPPORT_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme Pro offers the ability to produce CMYK color separations. This includes on-screen preview of CMYK and spot color plates, PANTONE® color support, spot colors, on-screen printer gamut preview and a lot more. Xtreme is now able to produce professional CMYK print results either via <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=17\">PDF/X</a> support or via direct&nbsp;four color and spot-color separation via the print dialog. <br />\r\n<br />Both options include crop and printer\'s marks. The direct separations printing includes control over print screening and screen types, emulsion side down and other advanced settings.','2008-04-07 17:54:24',1),(165,'FEATURE_COLOR_SEPARATION_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','CMYK;color separation;printing;spot color;pantone;','2008-04-07 17:54:24',0),(166,'FEATURE_DEFAULT','US','Xara Xtreme is simply the best <strong>graphics software</strong> for all your drawing and photo design&nbsp;needs, ideal for both print and the web.<br>\r\n<br>If you\'re looking for <strong>drawing software</strong> then Xtreme is a perfect solution for everything from simple logos to astonishingly detailed illustrations.<br>\r\n<br>If you\'re <strong>working with photos</strong> then Xtreme will match your ambitions from simple one click auto-enhance of your photo through to awesome photo compositions.<br>\r\n<br>If you are looking for software for creating <strong>web graphics</strong> then Xtreme can help you produce all the graphics you\'ll need for your site, from smart buttons to eye&nbsp;catching Flash animations&nbsp;and even complete HTML web pages and sites.<br>\r\n<br>Why not check out the examples of work by Xara artists in <strong><a title=\"\" target=\"_top\" href=\"/gallery/\">The Xara Gallery</a></strong>, from simple buttons to complete brochures.<br>\r\n<br>Whatever graphics you need and whatever your skill level, the famously friendly user interface and fast processing of Xara Xtreme will make it an absolute pleasure to be creative. And at a price that won\'t break the bank!','2009-05-22 13:33:46',1),(169,'FEATURE_PSD_SUPPORT_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme offers full support for importing and exporting Adobe Photoshop® PSD files including layer support (Xtreme layers are exported as PSD layers and PSD layers are imported as Xtreme layers), including alpha channel and (in Xtreme Pro only) 16-bit color and CMYK layer conversion. <br />\r\n<br />Adobe Photoshop® is the industry standard bitmap editing solution, and for many professionals Xtreme is their standard vector graphics tool. Now the two are more closely integrated than ever.','2008-04-07 17:53:46',1),(170,'FEATURE_PSD_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','PSD','2008-04-07 17:53:46',0),(171,'FEATURE_TEXT_H-LING_NAME','US','Text handling','2009-06-10 16:00:57',1),(172,'FEATURE_TEXT_H-LING_SHORT','US','The Text Tool allows you to enter text in lines, columns or even across multiple pages and gives you powerful control over the formatting, making Xara Xtreme an ideal tool for DTP projects like brochures and newsletters that combine drawings, photos and text.','2009-06-10 16:00:57',1),(173,'FEATURE_TEXT_H-LING_LONG','US','<p>The <strong>Text Tool</strong> allows you to enter as many lines of text as you want, at any place in your document. And Xara Xtreme\'s&nbsp;industry leading screen rendering&nbsp;makes it easier to read text on screen, especially at small sizes or rotated.</p>\r\n<p>You can enter your text at any angle and you can also <strong>set your text along a path -</strong>&nbsp;so you could draw a line or curve and make the text follow it, curves and all. Additionally, just like any drawn object in Xara Xtreme, you can grab hold of the corners of the text object and resize it on the page, and <strong>apply any of the effects</strong>, such as <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=44\">transparency</a>, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=49\">fills</a>, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=52\">molds</a> and so on - and yet the text remains editable.<br>\r\n<br>Like any word processing program, you&nbsp;have <strong>full control over the text style</strong> - you can change the&nbsp;font, size, color and justification of the text, alter the line spacing and kerning, and have bold, italic, superscript or subscript.&nbsp;Recent improvements to the text tool provide high-end DTP-like features, such as margin and tab control (left, center, right and decimal tabs), 1st line indent or outdent control to provide support for hanging indents such as numbered or bulleted lists, word and character count of text stories.\r\n<p>Xtreme supports three types of text object: Simple text, <strong>text columns</strong> and text areas. You can have linked flowing text stories across text areas and columns, in any order or direction.&nbsp; And it also supports <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=25\"><strong>multi-page documents</strong></a>, &nbsp;<strong>automated text flow around objects and, new in V5, anchored graphics, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=264\">spell checking</a> and automatic font embedding</strong>. This brings Xara Xtreme well into the Desk Top Publishing arena. Along with the lightning fast screen update, Xtreme is now perfect for producing documents such as brochures and flyers.</p>','2009-06-10 16:00:57',1),(174,'FEATURE_TEXT_H-LING_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-06-10 16:00:57',0),(180,'FEATURE_ZOOM_SHORT','US','The Zoom tool allows magnification up to 25,000%, perfect for detailed work. And it\'s super-fast and resolution independent too.\r\nIf this image was created in Photoshop with the same detail, the file would be 2000 x 3000 inches, take hundreds of megabytes of memory and file space. As a vector design it takes just 180Kbytes!','2008-05-01 14:02:15',1),(181,'FEATURE_ZOOM_LONG','US','The <strong>Zoom Tool</strong> allows you to alter the <strong>magnification</strong> of the current document, giving you a closer, or more distant view. <br />\r\n<br />Using the Zoom Tool you can zoom to the <strong>whole page</strong>, so you see the complete document, you can zoom to the <strong>drawing</strong>, which magnifies just the drawn image as opposed to the whole page, or you can select an object and then zoom to that <strong>selection</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />Another method is to zoom to a particular area by clicking and <strong>dragging</strong> the tool over the area. <br />\r\n<br />The Xara Xtreme Zoom Tool is capable of zooming in to <strong>25,601%</strong> - that\'s over <strong>25,000 dpi</strong> (dots per inch).','2008-05-01 14:02:15',1),(182,'FEATURE_ZOOM_KEYWORDS','US','zoom;','2008-05-01 14:02:15',0),(183,'FEATURE_ANTI-ALIASING_NAME','US','Anti-Aliasing','2009-05-21 17:13:18',1),(184,'FEATURE_ANTI-ALIASING_SHORT','US','Xara introduced the world\'s first vector anti-aliasing to bring maximum screen quality and is still a pioneer with the fastest, highest quality anti-aliasing available in any drawing program. \r\n','2009-05-21 17:13:18',1),(185,'FEATURE_ANTI-ALIASING_LONG','US','Xara introduced the <strong>world\'s first</strong> vector anti-aliasing to bring maximum screen quality. It still pioneers with the <strong>fastest, highest quality anti-aliasing</strong> available in any drawing program. <br>\r\n<br>Anti-aliasing <strong>improves the quality</strong> of on-screen images by <strong>smoothing the edges</strong> of objects. It does this by blending the edges with the background. This has the effect of smoothing lines and edges and of appearing to improve the resolution of the display. Anti-aliasing is particularly useful for <strong>web graphics</strong>. <br>\r\n<br>When you do use anti-aliasing in Xara Xtreme, it works in <strong>real-time</strong> so you can see the effect straight away. You can use anti-aliasing when working with <strong>vector</strong> images and <strong>bitmap</strong> images.','2009-05-21 17:13:18',1),(186,'FEATURE_ANTI-ALIASING_KEYWORDS','US','anti-aliasing','2009-05-21 17:13:18',0),(187,'FEATURE_COLOR_SUPPORT_NAME','US','Color support','2008-03-20 10:52:12',1),(188,'FEATURE_COLOR_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has a comprehensive, interactive color system. Simply drag colors from the color line to your object to change its colors, or drag across your object on screen to create a color gradient. Plus Xtreme\'s unique Linked Colors feature allows you to change all shades of a master color with a single click!','2008-03-20 10:52:12',1),(189,'FEATURE_COLOR_SUPPORT_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme has a <strong>comprehensive color system</strong> which enables you to alter the colors of objects directly or <strong>create your own colors</strong>, with names, which you can apply to multiple objects. <br />\r\n<br />With Xara Xtreme unique <strong>Linked Colors</strong> feature, it is very easy to create a drawing containing many shades of a color and with one alteration, immediately change the color of the whole picture.&nbsp;Simply pick a new&nbsp;master theme color and all linked shades and tones adjust automatically.<br />\r\n<br />You can work in <strong>CMYK</strong>, <strong>RGB</strong>, <strong>HSV</strong>, <strong>greyscale</strong> or <strong>Hexadecimal RGB</strong> web color mode. <br />\r\n<br />There is also a <strong>color&nbsp;sampler</strong> which, like an <strong>eye-dropper</strong>, you can use to select the color of any object on the screen, even in other applications,&nbsp;and easily apply it to other objects. Or just drag and drop colors from the color line onto an object to change its colors.</p>\r\n<p>The <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=49\"><strong>fill tool</strong></a> allows you to quickly and easily apply color graduations to any object, simply be clicking and dragging across the object,&nbsp; so&nbsp;like many features in Xara Xtreme, <strong>color editing is interactive and immediate</strong>.</p>','2008-03-20 10:52:12',1),(190,'FEATURE_COLOR_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','color;colour;linked;','2008-03-20 10:52:12',0),(191,'FEATURE_PRINTING_NAME','US','Printing','2008-04-07 10:51:24',1),(192,'FEATURE_PRINTING_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme provides a wide variety of options for printing your documents. ','2008-04-07 10:51:24',1),(193,'FEATURE_PRINTING_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme provides a wide variety of <strong>options</strong> for printing your documents. For example, you can choose paper orientation, how to fit images on the paper (including \'best fit\' and \'automatic fit\'), which layers to print and so on. You can display print borders and there\'s also a useful \'simulate print colors\' option to give you guidance on how your printed colors might look (compared to on screen colors).</p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme also supports <a href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=17\"><strong>PDF</strong></a> and PostScript output<strong>.</strong>&nbsp; <strong>Xara Xtreme</strong> <strong>Pro</strong> offers full <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=9\">color separation</a> support for commercial printing.</p>','2008-04-07 10:51:24',1),(194,'FEATURE_PRINTING_KEYWORDS','US','print;printing;','2008-04-07 10:51:24',0),(195,'FEATURE_PDF_SUPPORT_NAME','US','PDF Support','2009-05-21 15:31:32',1),(196,'FEATURE_PDF_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme offers industry leading export of super-clean, very compact PDF files (including support for graduated color fills and flat / graduated transparency). Combined with the PDF import feature, this provides another way to interchange files.','2009-05-21 15:31:32',1),(197,'FEATURE_PDF_SUPPORT_LONG','US','<p>Xara\'s <strong>PDF export</strong> tool creates super-clean, very compact PDF files. This includes support for graduated color fills, for flat transparency and graduated transparency.&nbsp; And&nbsp;when you export as PDF everything remains pixel perfect, resolution-independent vector graphics*.</p>\r\n<p>The PDF exporter has also been designed to allow the files to be opened by Adobe Illustrator®, so providing significantly improved Illustrator compatibility&nbsp;which means that&nbsp;vector artwork including graduated color and transparency can now be imported cleanly into Illustrator versions 9 onwards.</p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme also offers reliable <strong>PDF import</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>*PDF can only support the basic Xara graduated fill and transparency types of flat, linear and radial. Other graduated types are automatically rasterized (flattened) to any required resolution on export.</p>','2009-05-21 15:31:32',1),(198,'FEATURE_PDF_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','PDF;illustrator','2009-05-21 15:31:32',0),(199,'FEATURE_THE_DESIGNS_GALLERY_NAME','US','The Designs Gallery','2009-05-21 17:03:26',1),(200,'FEATURE_THE_DESIGNS_GALLERY_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme includes a Designs Gallery full of useful clipart, photos, ready-made templates and inspiring example illustrations.','2009-05-21 17:03:26',1),(201,'FEATURE_THE_DESIGNS_GALLERY_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme includes a Designs Gallery full of useful clipart, photos, ready-made <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=22\">templates</a> (such as cards, photo album layouts, stationery, web page layouts&nbsp;etc) and inspiring example illustrations, offering more than 3000 images in total. </p>\r\n<p>The example illustrations include inspirational drawings and photo work offered by existing owners of Xara Xtreme to demonstrate techniques and possibilities and the sheer variety of styles achievable. The gallery is updated regularly and new images can be downloaded directly to the gallery at any time. <br>\r\n<br>Xara Xtreme also includes a font and texture fill gallery including 250 TrueType and PostScript fonts and 500 textures.','2009-05-21 17:03:26',1),(202,'FEATURE_THE_DESIGNS_GALLERY_KEYWORDS','US','clipart;photos;textures;templates;illustrations;','2009-05-21 17:03:26',0),(203,'FEATURE_BITMAP_TRACER_NAME','US','Bitmap Tracer','2008-03-25 09:45:52',1),(204,'FEATURE_BITMAP_TRACER_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme’s powerful bitmap tracer can convert your bitmaps – typically photos, line-art or logos – into editable vector shapes.','2008-03-25 09:45:52',1),(205,'FEATURE_BITMAP_TRACER_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme’s powerful bitmap tracer can <strong>convert your bitmaps</strong> – typically photos, line-art or logos – <strong>into editable vector shapes</strong>. The Tracer offers great flexibility, with control over the number of colors, the fidelity of the trace to the original and a useful ‘noise’ cleaner that can remove imperfections from your bitmap (for example caused by scanning photos). So if for example you need to edit your logo and all if you have is a bitmap, all is not lost!','2008-03-25 09:45:52',1),(206,'FEATURE_BITMAP_TRACER_KEYWORDS','US','bitmap;trace;tracer;','2008-03-25 09:45:52',0),(207,'FEATURE_PROFILES_NAME','US','Profiles','2008-04-07 10:55:31',1),(208,'FEATURE_PROFILES_SHORT','US','When adding a blend, transparency, contour, fill or shadow to an object, you can change the attributes or properties of the effect by using the Profile dialog box. ','2008-04-07 10:55:31',1),(209,'FEATURE_PROFILES_LONG','US','When adding a <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=45\">blend</a>, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=44\">transparency</a>, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=47\">contour</a>, <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=49\">fill</a> or <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=50\">shadow</a> to an object, you can change the <strong>attributes</strong> or <strong>properties</strong> of the effect by using the Profile dialog box. <br />\r\n<br />What the Profile dialog box actually allows you to do depends on which effect is being used, but in all cases, you can either choose one of the <strong>set profiles</strong> or use the sliders to <strong>create your own</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />With transparency and fills you can change the&nbsp;<strong>rate or shape of change</strong>&nbsp;from start to end, while with blends and contours you can alter how the <strong>steps</strong> are spaced and how attributes like the colors, line thickness and transparencies are used. With shadows you can change the rate of change of transparency across shadow.&nbsp;It\'s all about giving you that extra little bit of control over your effects that can make all the difference.<br />\r\n<br />Altogether, the Profile dialog box makes a very <strong>powerful</strong> tool to help get your graphics just right.','2008-04-07 10:55:31',1),(210,'FEATURE_PROFILES_KEYWORDS','US','profile;profiles;','2008-04-07 10:55:31',0),(211,'FEATURE_NAME_GALLERY_NAME','US','Name Gallery','2008-02-26 13:06:10',1),(212,'FEATURE_NAME_GALLERY_SHORT','US','The Xara Xtreme Name Gallery lists all fonts, bitmaps, colors and Named Objects in a document, making document management easy.','2008-02-26 13:06:10',1),(213,'FEATURE_NAME_GALLERY_LONG','US','The <strong>unique</strong> and <strong>powerful</strong> Name Gallery sees an end to the days when graphic designers had to put each object within their image on a separate layer, just so they could easily select them when they wanted to make an alteration. <br />\r\n<br />The Xara Xtreme <strong>Name Gallery</strong> automatically lists all fonts, bitmaps, colors and Named Objects in a document - and you can name <strong>any object</strong> or <strong>group of objects</strong> within a document. It means you are able to see at a glance all the objects you have in a document and you can then use the Name Gallery to <strong>select</strong> objects you want just by clicking on their name in the list. <br />\r\n<br />You can also edit objects at <strong>group</strong> level - for example, you could change all the occurrences of Times New Roman within a document and apply a shadow to each instance. This <strong>saves valuable time</strong> because in the past each item would have to be edited individually. <br />\r\n<br />When naming <strong>grouped objects</strong>, you can then make group alterations, or export them all in a particular way.','2008-02-26 13:06:10',1),(214,'FEATURE_NAME_GALLERY_KEYWORDS','US','name gallery;','2008-02-26 13:06:10',0),(215,'FEATURE_TEMPLATES_NAME','US','Templates','2009-05-21 17:03:54',1),(216,'FEATURE_TEMPLATES_SHORT','US','Xtreme is ideal for creating your own designs from scratch of course, but it also includes a large and varied collection of templates that are an absolute snap to adjust to your own message, including greetings cards for every occasion, business stationery of every sort (letterheads, business cards etc), photo frames and web page designs.','2009-05-21 17:03:54',1),(217,'FEATURE_TEMPLATES_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme is ideal for creating your own designs from scratch of course, but&nbsp;the Xtreme CD&nbsp;also includes a large and varied collection of professionally designed, ready-made templates that are an absolute snap to customize with your own message.</p>\r\n<p>Templates include greetings cards for every occasion, business stationery of every sort (letterheads, business cards etc), photo frames, a large selection of photo album layouts,&nbsp;newsletters and newspapers, calendars, web page designs&nbsp;and many more categories. If you have the Xtreme trial, can see a small selection of the total set in the Designs Gallery (click Get&nbsp;Designs to download them).</p>\r\n<p>Simply enter your own text and/or drop in your own photo (enhanced in the integrated photo tool if necessary)&nbsp;and you can have professional looking results in minutes. It’s even easy to change the colors, using Xara Xtreme’s unique <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=15\">Color Linking</a> feature (just change the master theme color and all linked shades and tones adjust automatically). All templates are designed using Linked Colors.</p>','2009-05-21 17:03:54',1),(218,'FEATURE_TEMPLATES_KEYWORDS','US','templates;template;','2009-05-21 17:03:54',0),(219,'FEATURE_PANTONE_COLOR_SUPPORT_NAME','US','PANTONE® color support','2008-02-26 13:09:04',1),(220,'FEATURE_PANTONE_COLOR_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme Pro includes PANTONE® color libraries for use as both spot color and PANTONE® process color equivalents. ','2008-02-26 13:09:04',1),(221,'FEATURE_PANTONE_COLOR_SUPPORT_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme Pro includes PANTONE® color libraries for use as both spot color and PANTONE® process color equivalents.','2008-02-26 13:09:04',1),(222,'FEATURE_PANTONE_COLOR_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','Pantone;','2008-02-26 13:09:04',0),(223,'IMG_FEATURE_PANTONE','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/pantone.jpg\" />','2008-02-19 16:23:26',0),(976,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WHATSNEWXTREMEPRO','US','','2008-10-07 17:43:02',1),(977,'FEATURE_CAT_WN_HEADLINE','US','Headline new features','2008-03-07 18:50:13',1),(978,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WN_HEADLINE','US','','2008-03-07 18:50:13',1),(979,'FEATURE_CAT_WN_OTHER','US','Other enhancements','2008-03-07 18:50:06',1),(980,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WN_OTHER','US','','2008-03-07 18:50:06',1),(981,'FEATURE_CAT_WN_MINOR','US','Other minor improvements','2008-03-07 18:50:45',1),(225,'IMG_FEATURE_PSD','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/psd.gif\" />','2008-02-19 16:22:22',0),(226,'FEATURE_PDFX_EXPORT_NAME','US','PDF/X export','2009-05-21 15:49:59',1),(227,'FEATURE_PDFX_EXPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme Pro offers comprehensive PDF support, including full PDF/X export for professional users.','2009-05-21 15:49:59',1),(228,'FEATURE_PDFX_EXPORT_LONG','US','PDF has become the industry standard way of transferring documents of all types from one person to another, ensuring exact WYSIWYG fidelity.<br>\r\n<br>Xara Xtreme Pro&nbsp;offers class-leading PDF support including these features:\r\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Choice of PDF version from version 1.3 through to version 1.7, as well as PDF/X-1a 2001, x-1a 2003, X3-2002, and X-3 2003 standards.</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Full support for vector transparency (PDF version 1.4 or later)</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Font embedding and font subsetting options</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Export any selected page range</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Optional down-sampling of large bitmaps (reduces the size of PDFs for designs containing large photos)</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Full control over bitmap embedding options and compression (native, Flate, JPEG)</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Full control over bitmap transparency flattening, bitmap effect rasterization, to any required resolution and compression type</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Embedding of native JPG files for lossless JPEG transfer</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Support for Adobe Reader Layers. For PDF 1.5 and above you can now output and control Xtreme\'s layer visibility in Adobe Reader</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">File embedding. You can embed .xar files into your PDF and launch them from Adobe Reader</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Full pre-press PDF/X support including:\r\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Embedding page crop and printer\'s marks</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">ICC color profiles, including all the common paper stock options (e.g. US Web coated, ISO, etc)</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Embedding of custom ICC profiles</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Document encryption, with full control over document permissions:\r\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Password protect any PDF file, with 40 or 128-bit encryption</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Control over exact permissions, e.g. allow / disallow printing or commenting or text copying or extraction.</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Spot color support</td></tr></tbody></table>Thankfully for those that do not require such full control over PDF features, Xtreme Pro provides a simple choice of 4 typical PDF profiles for the novice user: Draft, Email, High Quality and Commercial Printing,&nbsp;as well as&nbsp;the option for custom settings.','2009-05-21 15:49:59',1),(1486,'SWF_CLIP_SWF','US','<div id=\"SWF_CLIP_SWF\" style=\"border:1px #797979 solid; width:380px; height:260px;\">Please install Flash&reg; and turn on Javascript.</div>\n			<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n			// <![CDATA[\n			var so = new SWFObject(\"/files/swf/us/clip.swf\", \"SWF_CLIP_SWF\", \"380\", \"260\", \"8\");\n			so.addParam(\"wmode\", \"transparent\");\n			so.write(\"SWF_CLIP_SWF\");\n			// ]]>\n			</script>','2008-03-21 22:43:15',0),(229,'FEATURE_PDFX_EXPORT_KEYWORDS','US','PDF','2009-05-21 15:49:59',0),(230,'FEATURE_MULTI-PAGE_DOCUMENTS_NAME','US','Multi-page documents','2010-01-21 15:54:58',1),(231,'FEATURE_MULTI-PAGE_DOCUMENTS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme includes support for multiple page documents, which makes Xtreme a great option for producing leaflets, newsletters and more.','2010-01-21 15:54:58',1),(232,'FEATURE_MULTI-PAGE_DOCUMENTS_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme&nbsp;includes support for <strong>multiple page documents</strong>, which makes Xtreme&nbsp;a great option for producing&nbsp;<strong>leaflets, newsletters</strong> and more. Pages can be single or double page spreads (left and right sides) and are arranged vertically, like a word processor or DTP program. Flexible controls include the ability to change individual page sizes and, via the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=262\">Object Gallery</a> (new in V5) easily re-order, add or delete pages&nbsp;in your document.&nbsp; Combined with the powerful <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=11\">text controls</a> this makes Xtreme a great choice for any DTP task.<br>\r\n<br>Xtreme\'s ultra-fast rendering means you can scroll through pages quickly and smoothly, even on large documents.\r\n<p>Multi-page documents can also be used in combination with the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=84\">HTML feature</a> to create <strong>multi-page websites</strong>.</p>','2010-01-21 15:54:58',1),(233,'FEATURE_MULTI-PAGE_DOCUMENTS_KEYWORDS','US','DTP;page;layout;multi;','2010-01-21 15:54:58',1),(234,'FEATURE_SHORTCUT_KEY_CONFIGURATION_NAME','US','Shortcut key configuration','2008-04-01 14:13:43',1),(235,'FEATURE_SHORTCUT_KEY_CONFIGURATION_SHORT','US','Users can configure the Xara Xtreme Pro key shortcuts and save / load configurations. ','2008-04-01 14:13:43',1),(236,'FEATURE_SHORTCUT_KEY_CONFIGURATION_LONG','US','Users can configure the Xara Xtreme Pro key shortcuts and save / load custom configurations (for example to achieve compatability with another program).','2008-04-01 14:13:43',1),(237,'FEATURE_SHORTCUT_KEY_CONFIGURATION_KEYWORDS','US','key shortcut;short-cut;short cut;','2008-04-01 14:13:43',0),(238,'FEATURE_XPS_SUPPORT_NAME','US','XPS Support','2008-10-07 17:27:18',1),(239,'FEATURE_XPS_SUPPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme Pro supports XPS export (and has a beta XPS import filter). This is an entirely new ‘page description’ file format invented by Microsoft that\'s vector based, and so is ideal as a resolution-independent portable document format.','2008-10-07 17:27:18',1),(240,'FEATURE_XPS_SUPPORT_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme Pro supports <strong>XPS export (and includes a beta import filter)</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>XPS is an entirely new ‘page description’ file format invented by Microsoft. The benefit of XPS format is that it’s vector based, and so is ideal as a resolution-independent portable document format. Fonts are embedded into the document and so you are assured of a very high quality WYSIWYG document. If you’re using Windows Vista you can view and print these document directly. If you’re using older versions of Windows you can obtain a free XPS Viewer download from the Microsoft web site to provide viewing and printing of these files. <br>\r\n<br>It should be noted that the Xara XPS export does not use the Microsoft standard XPS print system, but writes XPS files directly which ensures a far higher fidelity, and far smaller XPS files. <br>\r\n<br>XPS supports advanced vector features such as transparency, CMYK colors and embedded fonts.','2008-10-07 17:27:18',1),(241,'FEATURE_XPS_SUPPORT_KEYWORDS','US','XPS','2008-10-07 17:27:18',0),(242,'FEATURE_EXTERNAL_PHOTO_EDITORS_NAME','US','External Photo Editors','2008-03-21 21:02:42',1),(243,'FEATURE_EXTERNAL_PHOTO_EDITORS_SHORT','US','If Xara Xtreme\'s integrated photo tool doesn\'t fit the bill, you can select any external photo editor, whether it\'s one of the two bundled options (Xara Picture Editor and MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer) or another editor such as Corel Paintshop Pro or Adobe Photoshop. ','2008-03-21 21:02:42',1),(244,'FEATURE_EXTERNAL_PHOTO_EDITORS_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme\'s <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=66\"><strong>integrated photo tool</strong></a>&nbsp;can handle&nbsp;all the most common photo requirements, such as control over brightness, sharpness and color saturation (including a one-click auto enhance option) photo panoramas and red eye removal.</p>\r\n<p>However Xtreme also offers <strong>the ability to select an external photo editor</strong> -&nbsp;whether it\'s one of the two bundled options (Xara Picture Editor and MAGIX Xtreme Photo&nbsp;Designer or any external editor such as Corel Paintshop Pro or Adobe Photoshop. What\'s more, Xtreme monitors the photo file being edited, and detects when it\'s updated by the photo editor and then re-imports it back into Xtreme - and that means you can continue to have your photo editor open while working on the drawing in Xtreme. So whenever the image file is updated in your photo editor (when you click Save) your drawing is updated showing you the updated picture in context.</p>','2008-03-21 21:02:42',1),(245,'FEATURE_EXTERNAL_PHOTO_EDITORS_KEYWORDS','US','adobe photoshop;paint shop pro; corel photo paint;magix xtreme photo designer; xara picture editor; xara photo editor','2008-03-21 21:02:42',0),(246,'FEATURE_THE_XPE_PHOTO_EDITOR_NAME','US','The XPE Photo Editor','2008-03-21 21:02:07',1),(247,'FEATURE_THE_XPE_PHOTO_EDITOR_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme includes the integrated Xara Picture Editor, a supremely easy and fast photo editor which offers all the most commonly required photo editing tools.','2008-03-21 21:02:07',1),(248,'FEATURE_THE_XPE_PHOTO_EDITOR_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme includes the integrated Xara Picture Editor, a supremely easy and fast photo editor which offers all the most commonly required photo editing tools. A one click auto-enhancement feature takes the guesswork out of adjusting the brightness, contrast, color saturation and blur/sharpen of your digital photos. Plus XPE offers a red-eye removal tool, and intuitive crop and rotate tools. <br />\r\n<br />This sort of \'photo repair\' may account for the majority of your photo work but it could just be the beginning. XPE also supports third party plug-ins, including an enormous range of Adobe Photoshop® plug-ins, which allow you to add numerous effects to your photos, from the subtle and beautiful to the weird and wonderful. And Xtreme\'s drawing, editing and text tools can all be used, for example for adding a frame or a caption or watermark (see our tutorials) or for more advanced photo composition work. <br />\r\n<br />The basic picture editing operations can be done more quickly and easily than with other editors thanks to an innovative user interface of the Xara Picture Editor. As you manipulate the controls the changes are reflected immediately on the picture - no OK buttons required. <br />\r\n<br />No menus, fewer dialogs, fewer clicks means a more productive, more pleasurable way of working.','2008-03-21 21:02:07',1),(249,'FEATURE_THE_XPE_PHOTO_EDITOR_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-21 21:02:07',0),(250,'FEATURE_SINGLE_CLICK_AUTO-ENHANCE_NAME','US','Single click auto-enhance','2008-03-20 14:20:32',1),(251,'FEATURE_SINGLE_CLICK_AUTO-ENHANCE_SHORT','US','The integrated photo tool provides an automatic single-click enhance which can improve almost all badly exposed images.','2008-03-20 14:20:32',1),(252,'FEATURE_SINGLE_CLICK_AUTO-ENHANCE_LONG','US','Many photographs from digital cameras are under-exposed - too dark. Making individual adjustments of brightness, contrast, and color controls can be both time consuming and a confusing process for a great many users. The&nbsp;integrated photo tool&nbsp;provides an automatic single-click enhance which can instantly&nbsp;improve almost all badly exposed images (although you can still manually adjust the brightness, contrast, sharpness and color saturation individually if you wish to).','2008-03-20 14:20:32',1),(253,'FEATURE_SINGLE_CLICK_AUTO-ENHANCE_KEYWORDS','US','photo;photos;bitmaps;enhance;brightness;contrast;sharpness;blur;','2008-03-20 14:20:32',0),(254,'FEATURE_CROP_-_ROTATE_NAME','US','Crop &amp; Rotate','2009-05-21 16:18:37',1),(255,'FEATURE_CROP_-_ROTATE_SHORT','US','The integrated photo tool offers supremely intuitive crop and rotate tools, and Xara’s unique photo handling technology means that it’s real-time, interactive and completely smooth.','2009-05-21 16:18:37',1),(256,'FEATURE_CROP_-_ROTATE_LONG','US','<p>The Xara Xtreme integrated&nbsp;photo tool&nbsp;offers supremely intuitive <strong>crop and rotate</strong> tools, and Xara’s unique photo handling technology means that it’s <strong>real-time, interactive and completely smooth</strong>. </p>\r\n<p>To crop your photo simply select the Photo Tool, then click and drag over your photo to define the crop area, which can be subsequently repositioned or resized. And you can uncrop a photo later – even after it’s been saved! Rotating a photo is even easier - just click the rotate arrows.</p>','2009-05-21 16:18:37',1),(257,'FEATURE_CROP_-_ROTATE_KEYWORDS','US','crop;photo;photos;bitmap;clip;','2009-05-21 16:18:37',0),(258,'FEATURE_RED_EYE_REMOVAL_NAME','US','Red Eye Removal','2009-05-21 17:09:39',1),(259,'FEATURE_RED_EYE_REMOVAL_SHORT','US','The integrated photo tool offers an intuitive red eye removal tool.','2009-05-21 17:09:39',1),(260,'FEATURE_RED_EYE_REMOVAL_LONG','US','One of the most common requirements for anyone working with photos is red eye removal. The photo tool&nbsp;in Xara Xtreme offers an integrated, intuitive red eye removal tool that is&nbsp;fast and simple.','2009-05-21 17:09:39',1),(261,'FEATURE_RED_EYE_REMOVAL_KEYWORDS','US','redeye;red eye;photo;photos;bitmaps;','2009-05-21 17:09:39',0),(262,'FEATURE_MAINTAINING_PHOTO_QUALITY_NAME','US','Maintaining Photo Quality','2008-04-07 17:57:44',1),(263,'FEATURE_MAINTAINING_PHOTO_QUALITY_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme offers unique non-destructive editing of photos - that means you can edit your photo as many times as you like without the loss of quality that is normal in other photo programs.','2008-04-07 17:57:44',1),(264,'FEATURE_MAINTAINING_PHOTO_QUALITY_LONG','US','<p>A fundamental problem with conventional photo editing software is that each time you load and save a JPEG image, it deteriorates slightly. Load and save an image more than a few times and this becomes noticeable. This <strong>cumulative distortion</strong> is unavoidable if you use JPEG format photos. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Xara Xtreme overcomes this problem</strong> by keeping a track of the original \'master\' image, much like keeping a photographic negative. When you re-load any JPEG photo saved from Xtreme, it finds the original master and uses that as the source for all further processing, so Xtreme\'s photo editing is <strong>\'non-destructive\'</strong>. It remembers all edits you ever performed to any photo and lets you <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=34\"><strong>undo</strong></a> or alter those at any time. </p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme has another trick to help with photo quality - a new bi-cubic photo display that considerably <strong>improves the on-screen quality of scaled down photos</strong> compared with all other photo software.&nbsp;Simply select the&nbsp;\'very high quality\' option on the View Quality slider.</p>','2008-04-07 17:57:44',1),(265,'FEATURE_MAINTAINING_PHOTO_QUALITY_KEYWORDS','US','photo;photos;bitmaps;non-destructive;photo quality;jpeg;','2008-04-07 17:57:44',0),(266,'FEATURE_MAGIC_UNDO_NAME','US','Magic undo','2008-03-20 14:17:42',1),(267,'FEATURE_MAGIC_UNDO_SHORT','US','By keeping track of the original master photo and a list of edits performed, the Xara Xtreme offers the seemingly magic ability to undo changes to saved photos. ','2008-03-20 14:17:42',1),(268,'FEATURE_MAGIC_UNDO_LONG','US','By keeping track of the original master photo and a list of edits performed, Xara Xtreme&nbsp;offers the seemingly magic ability to <strong>undo changes to saved photos</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />Say you\'ve altered the brightness of a photo and saved the result. If you load this in the future you can undo the brightness change. This does not take the saved image and alter the brightness (that would result in cumulative distortion). Instead it re-creates a new image, identical to the one just loaded, from the original master. Perfect copies every time, plus the ability to alter or undo any edit <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Un-crop</strong><br />\r\nTry this with any other photo editing software:<br />\r\n• Load a photo, crop just a small section and save this cropped image<br />\r\n• Quit the program<br />\r\n• Now load the cropped version back in and try to Undo or recover the cropped parts. <br />\r\n<br />With Xara Xtreme you can!','2008-04-03 14:42:02',1),(269,'FEATURE_MAGIC_UNDO_KEYWORDS','US','photo;photos;bitmap;undo;','2008-03-20 14:17:42',0),(270,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_NAME','US','File Size','2008-04-02 16:57:18',1),(271,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme\'s unique way of handling and storing photos (lossless vector-based photo editing, combined with embedding the original JPEG) means that files containing photos can be anywhere from 3 to 100 times smaller than with other programs.','2008-04-02 16:57:18',1),(272,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme embeds your master JPEG in the Xara file, resulting in <strong>huge file size savings</strong>. A 5 Megapixel JPEG photo from a digital camera would expand to be typically 20Mbytes in other graphics programs. Use two or three such photos in your image, or make copies to edit and you\'ve now got a file that might easily be 60Mbytes large. The Xara Xtreme file will be <strong>ten times smaller</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>This plus the amazingly compact nature of Xara Xtreme’s native file format means that such files are much faster to save and reload. The instant redraw makes working with photos a pleasure, even photos from modern, very high resolution cameras. And this is an added bonus if you are exchanging files via email with other Xara Xtreme owners.</p>','2008-04-02 16:57:18',1),(273,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_KEYWORDS','US','photo;photos;compression;bitmap;','2008-04-02 16:57:18',0),(274,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_NAME','US','MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer','2008-03-21 21:01:10',1),(275,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_SHORT','US','MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer is a photo editor that is bundled with Xtreme.','2008-03-21 21:01:10',1),(276,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_LONG','US','<p>MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer is a photo editor that is bundled with Xtreme. In the latest versions of Xtreme it is possible to select Photo Designer or any other external photo editors of your choice. We have included some brief details below on MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer from the Magix website.<br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nAdd gloss to your pictures or teleport yourself from your garden to the south seas with the photo montage function. Transform your photos into artistic oil paintings and convert your living room into a gallery with your own pictures. At last you can make your creative ideas reality in just a few mouse clicks. With MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer you can easily get the very best out of your photos because professional results can be so easy. </p>\r\n<h1>Your advantages!</h1>\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"544\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p><img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"60\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/det_bearb_Kopie.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\"></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Professional editing<br />\r\n</strong>Panorama photos, photo montage, cropping, airbrushing...</p></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p><img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"80\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/emo_usecase-art.gif\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\"></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Artistic distortion<br />\r\n</strong>Innovative art-photo effects for oil paintings, caricatures, mosaic and pencil drawings...</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"7\" height=\"20\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p><img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/bildimbild_1.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Picture-in-picture<br />\r\n</strong>Realistic photo montages,<br />\r\ntext fields that disappear into the background...</p></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/bildschirm.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Effortless optimization<br />\r\n</strong>Auto-contrast, auto-color, brightness, saturation, gamma correction, focus...</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"7\" height=\"20\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p><img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"80\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/Textbild_fc.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Individual designs<br />\r\n</strong>Easy-to-use text editor with shadow and 3D effects...</p></td>\r\n<td width=\"10\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"80\">\r\n<p><img height=\"53\" alt=\"\" width=\"80\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/emo_usecase-present.gif\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"2\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n<p><strong>Versatile presentations</strong><br />\r\nPrint multiple pictures on one page, desktop pictures...</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<div class=\"dotline_bottom\"></div><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<h1>Powerful effects &amp; functions</h1>Lots of options – easy handling:\r\n<h3>Image optimization</h3>Use the handy 1-click automations like Auto Color and Auto Brightness, or correct your pictures precisely to the pixel. You can also easily optimize complete photo series using batch processing. MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer offers you solutions for your pictures\' optimal performance.\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"95\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/rote_augen_180.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"15\"></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"95\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/belichtung_180.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"15\"></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"95\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/farben_kontrast_180.jpg\" /></p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Remove red-eye</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Optimize brightness</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Refresh colors and contrast</p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"15\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" />\r\n<h3>Detailed picture editing</h3>You can master even difficult tasks easily. Restore your old pictures, or remove creases, add vacation tans, or whiten teeth like a plastic surgeon. You\'ll be amazed how easy these operations are with <strong>MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer.</strong>\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td></tr>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/freistellen_klein.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img height=\"95\" alt=\"\" width=\"93\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/restauration_klein.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img height=\"95\" alt=\"\" width=\"93\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/heller_klein.jpg\" /></p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Crop people/objects</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Restore Photos </p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Brighten areas</p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"15\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" />&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Individual picture creation</h3>MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer contains a high-performance creative suite – packed full with useful tools and effects, just waiting for you to be put to use. Funny caricatures, artistic paintings or photo montages filled with amazing effects, the numerous presets deliver impressive results, which can always be adjusted to your taste.\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"73\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/logo_funny_180.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"15\"></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"73\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/logo_painting_180.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"15\"></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"73\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/logo_montage_180.jpg\" /></p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Funny caricatures</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Artistic paintings</p></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n<p>Striking photo montages</p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"15\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<h3>Useful effect overview</h3>The handy effect browser shows you all the effects with clear and descriptive examples. Select one of the numerous effects and your photo turns into a creative expression. If you want, you can apply the effect precisely to a specific picture area using the paintbrush.\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#ffffff\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"575\" align=\"center\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">\r\n<p><img height=\"91\" alt=\"\" width=\"575\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/compo_oneclick-fx_575.jpg\" /></p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Color balance</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Color gradient</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Negative</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Poster</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Red/Green/Blue</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"95\">\r\n<p>Tone/Saturation</p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"15\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<h3>Panorama pictures at a click</h3>With <strong>MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer</strong> you can easily create panorama pictures all by yourself! The integrated panorama picture assistant helps you seamlessly attach the individual pictures of your panorama-to-be to one another. Simply import your pictures, optimize the picture transitions, and you\'re done. In just a few clicks you can turn your individual pictures into tailor-made panorama pictures.\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"116\" alt=\"\" width=\"145\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/screen_panorama.jpg\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"49\"></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><img height=\"116\" alt=\"\" width=\"381\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/compo_panorama.jpg\" /></p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"15\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<h3>Easy to use without previous experience</h3>If you want, you can switch on the interactive Task Assistant which will explain the most important functions. Whether it\'s brightening areas, cropping people or objects, removing tears or scratches, transforming your pictures into paintings or artistically distorting them, our Assistant will bring you straight to the function without any cumbersome searching. With the help of the practical 1-2-3 direct</td>\r\n<td width=\"15\"></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">\r\n<p><img height=\"204\" alt=\"\" width=\"165\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/screen_optimierung_uk.jpg\" /></p></td></tr></tbody></table><img class=\"spacer-gif\" title=\"\" height=\"10\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" src=\"/img/global/1px.gif\" /><br />\r\n<div></div>','2008-03-21 21:01:10',1),(277,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_KEYWORDS','US','MAGIX Xtreme Photo Designer;','2008-03-21 21:01:10',0),(306,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_NAME','US','Transparency','2009-05-21 16:38:45',1),(278,'FEATURE_PHOTO_H-LING_OVERVIEW_NAME','US','Photo Handling Overview','2008-05-01 14:04:11',1),(279,'FEATURE_PHOTO_H-LING_OVERVIEW_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme photo handling beats other graphics programs on many fronts: It\'s much, much faster, produces files that can be 10x or more smaller. \r\nBeing entirely object oriented means completely non-destructive photo editing, and uses a fraction of the RAM required by other products. It can handle multiple very high resolution images with ease, even on a modest PC. It makes the perfect photo composition tool.','2008-05-01 14:04:11',1),(280,'FEATURE_PHOTO_H-LING_OVERVIEW_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme photo and bitmap handling is <strong>faster and more powerful</strong> than you\'ll find in other graphics programs. Xara Xtreme uses <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=35\"><strong>compression techniques</strong></a> that means that Xara files including photos can be up to ten times smaller than equivalent images in other drawing programs, with enormous benefits for speed and usability.&nbsp; Plus Xara\'s unique <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=33\"><strong>non-destructive editing</strong></a> maintains the high quality of your original photo, however many times you edit it, and gives you the ability to <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=34\"><strong>undo</strong></a> any&nbsp;edits you\'ve made to your photo, even after saving and reloading. As a result many people use Xara Xtreme as their primary, general purpose image composition tool. </p>\r\n<p>Almost anything you can do to vector&nbsp;drawings you can also&nbsp;do to photos/bitmaps in Xtreme. For example, you can edit the shape, <strong>alter the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=44\">transparency</a></strong>, including graduated transparency, <strong>use bitmaps as <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=49\">fills</a></strong> on any shape, add a drop <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=50\">shadow</a></strong>, <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=46\">feather</a></strong> the edges and a lot more - all in real-time. </p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme <strong>supports all the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=8\">common bitmap formats</a>,</strong> for both import and export. Add to this the ability to handle <strong>multi-layer 32-bit alpha channel</strong> (semi-transparent) bitmaps and Xara Xtreme is a <strong>supreme image composition tool</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme also includes an <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=66\"><strong>integrated photo editing tool</strong></a>. We don\'t pretend this makes it either a painting program or pixel editor but it does provide the most common photo editing features such as <strong>cropping</strong>, <strong>rotating</strong>, <strong>enhancing</strong>, <strong>sharpening</strong>, <strong>red-eye removal</strong> etc with a fast, interactive, <strong>live-preview</strong> of all edits.&nbsp;Plus the new V4&nbsp;includes an effective <strong>photo panorama</strong> creator. The photo tool&nbsp;will continue to grow in capabilities with future releases of Xara Xtreme. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme includes a <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=19\">fast bitmap tracer</a></strong> to help convert bitmaps to vector shapes. </p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme also supports third party plug-ins such as <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=86\"><strong>Adobe Photoshop plug-ins</strong></a> to expand the range of available effects that you can apply to your photos.</p>\r\n<p>Finally Xtreme includes a collection of professionally designed, fully editable <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=22\"><strong>templates</strong></a> that include photo frames and&nbsp;photo album layouts.</p>','2008-05-01 14:04:11',1),(281,'FEATURE_PHOTO_H-LING_OVERVIEW_KEYWORDS','US','photo;photos;bitmap;bitmaps;','2008-05-01 14:04:11',0),(282,'FEATURE_RAW_PHOTO_IMPORT_NAME','US','RAW photo import','2009-06-02 16:36:03',1),(283,'FEATURE_RAW_PHOTO_IMPORT_SHORT','US','You can import RAW digital camera files (either using the Import menu option or just drag and drop the file onto the Xara Xtreme window).','2009-06-02 16:36:03',1),(284,'FEATURE_RAW_PHOTO_IMPORT_LONG','US','You can import RAW digital camera files (either using the Import menu option or just drag&nbsp;and drop the file onto the Xara Xtreme window). <br>\r\n<br><strong>Supported cameras (updated in V5)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<ul class=\"feature_bullets\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" />\r\n<o:p>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\">Adobe Digital Negative (DNG)</span> </li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple QuickTake 100\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li></o:p></span>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple QuickTake 150\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apple QuickTake 200\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">AVT F-080C\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">AVT F-145C\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">AVT F-201C\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">AVT F-510C\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">AVT F-810C\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Canon PowerShot 600\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US