00\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Sony DSLR-A900\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Sony XCD-SX910CR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">STV680 VGA\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>','2009-06-02 16:36:03',1),(285,'FEATURE_RAW_PHOTO_IMPORT_KEYWORDS','US','RAW;photo;photos;','2009-06-02 16:36:03',0),(286,'FEATURE_LEVELS_CONTROL_NAME','US','Levels control','2009-05-21 17:18:37',1),(287,'FEATURE_LEVELS_CONTROL_SHORT','US','For the advanced user, Xara Xtreme includes a powerful Photo Levels control to adjust brightness levels of images. ','2009-05-21 17:18:37',1),(288,'FEATURE_LEVELS_CONTROL_LONG','US','For the advanced user&nbsp;the integrated photo tool of Xara Xtreme&nbsp;now includes a Levels control to adjust brightness levels of images. This single controls offers: <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Histogram view of the brightness levels of the image</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Control over input black, white and gamma and output black and white levels. These controls provide a far more powerful way of adjusting brightness, contrast and gamma than the traditional simple brightness and contrast controls.</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Single click before and after compare</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Color correction e.g. to adjust for a color cast from using the wrong white balance settings</td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">• </td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\">Overlaid before and after histograms. As you adjust the levels you can see the original and the modified histogram (shown in red below).</td></tr></tbody></table>','2009-05-21 17:18:37',1),(289,'FEATURE_LEVELS_CONTROL_KEYWORDS','US','levels;photo;photos;','2009-05-21 17:18:37',0),(290,'FEATURE_DRAWING_TOOLS_NAME','US','Drawing Tools','2008-05-01 13:45:01',1),(291,'FEATURE_DRAWING_TOOLS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme is primarily a vector graphics application and includes a set of really easy vector line and shape editing tools.\r\nThe Freehand tool offers live smoothing after you\'ve drawn your line, along with the ability to edit any outlines.','2008-05-01 13:45:01',1),(292,'FEATURE_DRAWING_TOOLS_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme uses <strong>two types</strong> of drawing tools: <strong>Freehand tools</strong> and <strong>Shape tools</strong>. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>The Freehand tools </strong>allow you to hand-draw&nbsp;lines or shapes on the page.&nbsp;You can&nbsp;simply drag on the drawn&nbsp;lines to convert them into curves, or&nbsp;\'push\' and \'pull\' them in a very intuitive way.&nbsp;You can choose in advance how closely you want the computer to follow your movements, or&nbsp;you can&nbsp;smooth out any minor bumps with Xara Xtreme\'s <strong>retroactive smoothing.</strong> You can even draw one shape, then add another bit to it by drawing some more and joining up with the original object. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Shape tools</strong>, like the <strong>rectangle</strong>, <strong>circle/ellipse</strong> and <strong>Quickshape</strong> tools allow you to draw <strong>pre-set</strong> shapes very quickly and easily. <br />\r\n<br />Any object you create, either Freehand or Shape, can be resized or rotated by&nbsp;simply dragging its handles.','2008-05-01 13:45:01',1),(293,'FEATURE_DRAWING_TOOLS_KEYWORDS','US','drawing;freehand;shape;draw;lines;curves;','2008-05-01 13:45:01',0),(294,'FEATURE_DRAG_-_DROP_NAME','US','Drag and Drop','2008-05-01 13:28:55',1),(295,'FEATURE_DRAG_-_DROP_SHORT','US','Many tasks in Xara Xtreme benefit from being able to use the drag and drop principle, which is the most intuitive way of working and a great time saver. It also supports drag and drop import of files, such as photos.\r\n','2008-05-01 13:28:55',1),(296,'FEATURE_DRAG_-_DROP_LONG','US','<p>Many tasks in Xara Xtreme <strong>benefit</strong> from being able to use the drag and drop principle, which is more intuitive and a great time saver.</p>\r\n<p>For example, when changing the color of an object, you can just <strong>drag</strong> a color from the Color Line and <strong>drop</strong> it <strong>onto the object</strong>, or its outline.&nbsp; And with color&nbsp;gradients, you can drop colors along the gradient path and make <strong>multi-color fills</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />Drag and drop also comes into play when using the <strong>galleries</strong>. You can place <strong>any gallery item</strong> on a page simply by drag and drop.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Xtreme&nbsp;also supports drag and drop import of files, such as photos.</p>','2008-05-01 13:28:55',1),(297,'FEATURE_DRAG_-_DROP_KEYWORDS','US','drag and drop','2008-05-01 13:28:55',0),(298,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_NAME','US','Solid Object Dragging','2008-05-01 14:01:31',1),(299,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_SHORT','US','Instead of dragging outlines when you move, rotate or resize objects, Xtreme offers solid live object manipulation. Only Xtreme is fast enough to do this on complex vector graphics.','2008-05-01 14:01:31',1),(300,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme offers one of&nbsp;the world\'s first live solid dragging, scaling and rotating of objects, for the ultimate in WYSIWYG editing. That means that as you reposition, resize or rotate an object the whole object moves, rather than just an outline, making it far easier to judge the effect of your edits in real time.','2008-05-01 14:01:31',1),(301,'FEATURE_SOLID_OBJECT_DRAGGING_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-05-01 14:01:31',0),(302,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_NAME','US','Undo / Redo','2008-04-07 17:56:31',1),(303,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_SHORT','US','Being able to change what you have done is vital in a graphics package. Xara Xtreme allows unlimited undo, making experimentation easy.','2008-04-07 17:56:31',1),(304,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_LONG','US','Being able to change what you have done is <strong>vital</strong> in a graphics package. Xara Xtreme allows you to easily <strong>Undo</strong> your most recent changes to a document. <br />\r\n<br />Undo allows you to get rid of changes which you\'ve applied <strong>by mistake</strong>, those which went <strong>wrong</strong> or ones which you simply <strong>don\'t like</strong> the look of. Undo is a very powerful tool when combined with <strong>Redo</strong> because it gives you the <strong>freedom</strong> to <strong>experiment</strong> with a drawing, secure in the knowledge that you can always undo any changes or if you eventually decide you do actually like the changes, to redo them again. <br />\r\n<br />Some graphics packages only let you undo a <strong>limited</strong> amount of actions, but Xara Xtreme has an <strong>unlimited undo</strong> so it remembers <strong>everything</strong> you\'ve done.','2008-04-07 17:56:31',1),(305,'FEATURE_UNDO_REDO_KEYWORDS','US','undo;redo;','2008-04-07 17:56:31',0),(307,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_SHORT','US','Xara was the first vector application to introduce transparency, and continues to this day to offer the easiest, most advanced transparency control of any software. With click-drag simplicity you can create graduated blends to any object, photo, text, and vector shape.','2009-05-21 16:38:45',1),(308,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_LONG','US','<p>Any object you create (including text and bitmaps) can be made transparent using the <strong>wide variety of transparency options</strong> available. <br>\r\n<br>Like real-time anti-aliasing, Xara was the <strong>pioneer of vector transparency</strong>. Transparency can be used in a number of ways - one of the most common is to simulate glass, but it can also be used to create <strong>subtle reflections and highlights</strong> that are very difficult to achieve in any other way. <br>\r\n<br>Another common use is to overlay parts of your drawing with additional transparent objects which can then be used as <strong>filters</strong> to modify colors or contrast in your image, for example. Xara Xtreme also allows you to create <strong>textured transparencies</strong> by using bitmaps of your choice to give a special effect to any graphic or selection of graphics.\r\n<p>Transparency can be applied in a linear <strong>graduation</strong> or even a<strong> multi-stage graduation&nbsp;(new in V5).</strong>&nbsp;Plus there\'s a&nbsp;variety of shapes such as diamond or conical transparency to get some very unusual effects. Transparency can be applied in <strong>any direction</strong> and is <strong>independent of color</strong> - simply select the transparency tool and then click and drag on the image to apply the transparency, <strong>completely interactive and immediate</strong>.<br>\r\n<br>','2009-05-21 16:38:45',1),(309,'FEATURE_TRANSPARENCY_KEYWORDS','US','Transparency','2009-05-21 16:38:45',0),(310,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_NAME','US','Blend Tool','2008-04-02 16:39:28',1),(311,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_SHORT','US','The blend tool tweens or blends from one shape to another. It\'s ultra-fast, click-drag simple, works with vector shapes, text and photos.','2008-04-02 16:39:28',1),(312,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_LONG','US','<p>The Xara Xtreme <strong>Blend Tool</strong> allows you to blend or merge between any two objects. These objects can be any of the available object types (text, bitmaps, shapes), or even other blends. <br />\r\n<br />Using the tool creates a <strong>set of intermediate objects</strong> so you get a <strong>transition</strong> from the start object to the end object. You can change the number of steps in the blend and also have more than one stage so you can blend between several objects. <br />\r\n<br />Blends can be used to create <strong>complex highlights</strong>, <strong>blurred edges</strong> on objects, <strong>repetitive patterns</strong> and many other effects. You can even <strong>edit objects</strong> within the blend once you have created them. You can also set blends <strong>along a path</strong>, such as a curve. </p>\r\n<p>For fine tuning, blends also have a <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=20\">profile control</a> for&nbsp;adjusting the rate of change of steps and other attributes across the blend.<br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme performs blending in a very <strong>quick and memory-efficient</strong> way compared to other drawing packages - meaning less waiting for you and less draining of your systems resources.</p>','2008-04-02 16:39:28',1),(313,'FEATURE_BLEND_TOOL_KEYWORDS','US','blend;blending;merge;','2008-04-02 16:39:28',0),(314,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_NAME','US','Soft Vectors','2009-05-21 16:40:55',1),(315,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_SHORT','US','Xara was the first application to offer vector feathering, vector soft shadows.  It still has the most advanced and enables high quality realistic images to be created more quickly and easily than on any other software. \r\nFeathering, combined with transparency provides great photo compositing features, as well as great vector shading.\r\n','2009-05-21 16:40:55',1),(316,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_LONG','US','Soft vectors or \'feathering\' is a technique of slightly <strong>blurring the edges</strong> of objects&nbsp;to help them blend into the background - until&nbsp;recently impossible in vector drawing programs. <br>\r\n<br>Simply by selecting an object - <strong>any object</strong> including shapes, text, photos and even clipviews - and moving the slider on the feather bar, it makes the selected object <strong>merge</strong> into background objects and avoids a <strong>sharp line</strong> at the boundary. This is particularly useful when overlaying bitmaps. <br>\r\n<br>Xara Xtreme allows you to change the feathering <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=20\">profile</a></strong>, altering the <strong>transition</strong> across the feather. You might want a regular rate of change or a more pronounced change towards one end or the center. <br>\r\n<br>Note that feathering affects <strong>only</strong> the object\'s edge and no other part of the object.','2009-05-21 16:40:55',1),(317,'FEATURE_SOFT_VECTORS_KEYWORDS','US','feather;feathering;','2009-05-21 16:40:55',0),(318,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_NAME','US','Contours','2008-03-20 19:38:24',1),(319,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_SHORT','US','Creating contours around objects is easy with the Xara Xtreme Contour Tool. Contouring is a special effect which adds evenly-spaced concentric rings inside or outside an object. These rings can be made to fade in to the background, or progress through a rainbow of colors. ','2008-03-20 19:38:24',1),(320,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_LONG','US','Creating contours around objects is easy with the Xara Xtreme <strong>Contour Tool</strong>. Contouring is a <strong>special effect</strong> which adds <strong>evenly-spaced concentric rings</strong> inside or outside an object. These rings can be made to <strong>fade</strong> in to the background, or progress through a <strong>rainbow</strong> of colors. <br />\r\n<br />When you have applied a contour to an object, if you <strong>resize</strong> or <strong>alter</strong> the object, the contour changes with it. The contour itself can be <strong>edited</strong> and you can change any of its properties, including the distance between the steps, the number of steps, contour width and profile. <br />\r\n<br />The <strong>Inset Path</strong> button lets you <strong>convert</strong> your contoured object into a larger or smaller shape, removing the actual contours. This gives you more flexibility than simply resizing an object, as it deals with <strong>thickness</strong> as opposed to size.','2008-03-20 19:38:24',1),(321,'FEATURE_CONTOURS_KEYWORDS','US','contour;contours;contouring;','2008-03-20 19:38:24',0),(322,'FEATURE_BEVELS_NAME','US','Bevels','2008-03-20 18:09:37',1),(323,'FEATURE_BEVELS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme\'s bevel tools allows you to add realistic bevels to any object with a single click, giving them the realistic appearance of depth. ','2008-03-20 18:09:37',1),(324,'FEATURE_BEVELS_LONG','US','<p>Bevels give objects the <strong>appearance of depth</strong> instead of being flat on the page. They are particularly useful when creating <strong>buttons</strong> or <strong>headings</strong> for web pages. <br />\r\n<br />The Xara Xtreme <strong>Bevel Tool</strong> allows you to quickly apply customized bevels to <strong>any object</strong> you draw. There are a range of <strong>set bevel types</strong> to choose from, such as flat, frame and rounded, and each one can be altered to make it unique. You can alter the <strong>depth</strong>, <strong>contrast</strong> and <strong>lighting elevation</strong> (unique to Xara Xtreme) and <strong>angle</strong>, and you can choose whether the bevel should be <strong>inside</strong> or <strong>outside</strong> the object. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme also allows you to treat a bevel like you would any other object in a document - so you can apply transparencies, color bitmap fills and so on. And again, the Bevel Tool takes advantage of Xara Xtreme\'s <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=12\">direct action</a> feature.</p>\r\n<p>Bevels in Xara Xtreme are <strong>resolution independent</strong>, which means you can scale them without any loss of quality.</p>','2008-03-20 18:09:37',1),(325,'FEATURE_BEVELS_KEYWORDS','US','bevel;bevels;','2008-03-20 18:09:37',0),(326,'FEATURE_FILLS_NAME','US','Fills','2008-03-20 15:07:51',1),(327,'FEATURE_FILLS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme offers a very wide range of fills - flat, linear, circular etc. You can use colors, bitmaps, photos or fractal effects as fills and have multi-color or multi-stage fills. And they couldn\'t be easier to edit - simply drag the fill arrow to change the position or angle of the fill.','2008-03-20 15:07:51',1),(328,'FEATURE_FILLS_LONG','US','<p>You can fill an object with a color or multiple colors, or even with a photo, bitmap or fractal effect. Xara Xtreme offers a wide range of fill types&nbsp;- flat, linear, circular, conical, elliptical, diamond and three and four color fills.</p>\r\n<p>You can apply fills to <strong>Quickshapes</strong>, <strong>shapes</strong> and even <strong>text</strong>. If you apply a fill to a <strong>compound object</strong> (a blend, mold or group) it affects all the objects in it. <br />\r\n<br />Once you have applied a <strong>color fill</strong> to an object you can change its size, position, direction and the colors it uses as well as the way the colors change across the fill. With <strong>bitmap fills</strong> you can change the bitmap used and with <strong>fractal fills</strong> you can change the resolution and grain of the fractal. <br />\r\n<br />One of the strongest features of Xara Xtreme is the <strong>simple and interactive</strong> way that color fills can be applied and edited. Just drag a color from the color line and drop it onto the object you want to fill, then drag the fill arrow to adjust the position and angle of the fill or drop new colors onto the arrow to create a multi-stage fill. This <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=12\">direct action</a> makes working with fills much easier than&nbsp;any other graphics&nbsp;program.</p>','2008-03-20 15:07:51',1),(329,'FEATURE_FILLS_KEYWORDS','US','fill;fills;color;transparency;bitmap','2008-03-20 15:07:51',0),(330,'FEATURE_SHADOWS_NAME','US','Shadows','2008-03-21 14:14:31',1),(331,'FEATURE_SHADOWS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme\'s Shadow tool lets you apply, remove, and modify semi-transparent (or \'soft\') shadows to any object, with a single click. ','2008-03-21 14:14:31',1),(332,'FEATURE_SHADOWS_LONG','US','Creating realistic shadows has commonly been the realm of the bitmap graphics package. Xara Xtreme\'s <strong>Shadow Tool</strong> changes all that and lets you apply, remove, and modify semi-transparent (or \'soft\') shadows to any object, with a single click. The transparency of soft shadows increases towards the edge, which gives a very realistic effect. Shadows are resolution independent in Xara Xtreme, which means you can scale them without losing quality.<br />\r\n<br />There are <strong>three different shadow types</strong> to choose from - <strong>Wall</strong>, <strong>Floor</strong> and <strong>Glow</strong>. Wall shading produces drop shadow effects, the Floor option works like a sundial would and Glow creates a halo effect around an object. <br />\r\n<br />Any shadow you make can be <strong>manipulated</strong> in a number of ways, allowing you to change the color, blur, transparency and <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=20\">profile</a>. Again, the Shadow tool takes advantage of the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=12\">direct action</a> feature.','2008-03-21 14:14:31',1),(333,'FEATURE_SHADOWS_KEYWORDS','US','shadow;shadows;','2008-03-21 14:14:31',0),(334,'FEATURE_BRUSHES_NAME','US','Brushes','2008-03-21 22:44:00',1),(335,'FEATURE_BRUSHES_SHORT','US','The real-time brush feature of the Freehand and Brush Tool is a fun but extremely powerful feature. ','2008-03-21 22:44:00',1),(336,'FEATURE_BRUSHES_LONG','US','The real-time <strong>brush feature</strong> of the Freehand and Brush Tool is a <strong>fun</strong> but extremely <strong>powerful</strong> feature. <br />\r\n<br />It enables you to create any shape, then use it to \'<strong>draw</strong>\' with, giving endless possibilities. One such possibility is to create airbrush-like effects. There are also a number of <strong>pre-defined brushes</strong> that you can use. The brush feature\'s power lies in the fact that you have <strong>complete control</strong> over the way the brush paints to the screen. You can alter the size of instances, color, spacing, rotation and offset properties, and each of these has a randomize option which can give a less ordered look. <br />\r\n<br />When using brushes, you can also take advantage of Xara\'s <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=54\"><strong>pressure sensitive</strong></a> feature by setting the brush to adjust the scaling or transparency of brush strokes according to how hard you press with your graphic pen. <br />\r\n<br />Each brush you create is saved along with the document it\'s used in, so you can re-use them whenever you wish.','2008-03-21 22:44:00',1),(337,'FEATURE_BRUSHES_KEYWORDS','US','brush;brushes','2008-03-21 22:44:00',0),(338,'FEATURE_MOLDS_ENVELOPES_NAME','US','Molds / envelopes','2008-03-20 15:09:47',1),(339,'FEATURE_MOLDS_ENVELOPES_SHORT','US','Perspective and Envelope Molds allow you to distort any object you select according to a set shape - rather like a jello mold does. ','2008-03-20 15:09:47',1),(340,'FEATURE_MOLDS_ENVELOPES_LONG','US','Molds allow you to <strong>distort</strong> any object you select according to a set shape - rather like a <strong>jello mold</strong> does. <br />\r\n<br />There are <strong>two types</strong> of mold - <strong>Perspective Molds</strong> and <strong>Envelope Molds</strong>. Perspective Molds are ideal for <strong>creating banners</strong> and <strong>three-dimensional effects</strong>. They distort an object by making it appear to have perspective. With <strong>Envelope Molds</strong> you can have <strong>curved sides</strong> and you can distort and <strong>warp</strong> a shape using the four corners of the mold shape. <br />\r\n<br />Molds and Envelopes can be applied to shapes, bitmaps and text, and all objects remain editable.','2008-03-20 15:09:47',1),(341,'FEATURE_MOLDS_ENVELOPES_KEYWORDS','US','mold;mould;envelope;perspective;','2008-03-20 15:09:47',0),(342,'FEATURE_CLIPVIEW_NAME','US','ClipView','2008-03-21 22:44:19',1),(343,'FEATURE_CLIPVIEW_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has several ways of using objects to mask or clip other objects. You then see part of the objects through that mask. ','2008-03-21 22:44:19',1),(344,'FEATURE_CLIPVIEW_LONG','US','Xara Xtreme has several ways of using objects to \"mask\" or \"clip\" other objects. You then see part of the objects through that mask. <br />\r\n<br />ClipView is one of these methods, but it is different from the others because it is dynamic. It lets you use an object as a \'<strong>window</strong>\' onto other objects. You see only those parts of other objects that are <strong>within</strong> the window. We call this creating a ClipView. You can <strong>move</strong> the window object to change your <strong>view</strong> while the window object remains visible.','2008-03-21 22:44:19',1),(345,'FEATURE_CLIPVIEW_KEYWORDS','US','clip;clipview;mask;','2008-03-21 22:44:19',0),(346,'FEATURE_PRESSURE_SENSITIVITY_NAME','US','Pressure sensitivity','2008-03-20 15:10:50',1),(347,'FEATURE_PRESSURE_SENSITIVITY_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has made using a graphics tablet even more realistic, because now you get the advantage of pressure sensitivity. ','2008-03-20 15:10:50',1),(348,'FEATURE_PRESSURE_SENSITIVITY_LONG','US','The closest thing to actually drawing for real comes from using a <strong>graphics tablet</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />With Xara Xtreme using a graphics tablet can be&nbsp;<strong>even more realistic</strong>&nbsp;if you take&nbsp;advantage of the pressure sensitivity feature in the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=51\">Brush tool.</a> <br />\r\n<br />The Brush tool&nbsp;gives you the option of relating&nbsp;the <strong>size</strong> and/or the <strong>transparency</strong> of the brush&nbsp;stroke to the pressure&nbsp;applied&nbsp;to the pen.&nbsp;You can&nbsp;choose whether you want the pressure to affect scaling or transparency - or both, or neither.','2008-03-20 15:10:50',1),(349,'FEATURE_PRESSURE_SENSITIVITY_KEYWORDS','US','pressure','2008-03-20 15:10:50',0),(350,'FEATURE_LIVE_EFFECTS_NAME','US','Live Effects','2009-05-21 16:15:26',1),(351,'FEATURE_LIVE_EFFECTS_SHORT','US','Live Effects are plug-in effects that can be applied to any object, including vector drawings - they are called Live Effects because the vector object remains editable even after applying the effect. Most modern Photoshop plug-ins work as Live Effects.','2009-05-21 16:15:26',1),(352,'FEATURE_LIVE_EFFECTS_LONG','US','Live Effects are plug-in effects that can be applied to any object, including vector drawings. They are called Live Effects because the vector object remains editable after applying the effect - when you edit the object, the Live Effect is re-applied automatically to the new shape. <br>\r\n<br>Adobe Photoshop® plug-ins, both free and commercial, already exist for creating a range of effects that would take a lifetime to explore - metallic effects, color and image distortions, glows, water ripples, bevels etc etc. We have included a selection of the best Photoshop plug-ins that work as&nbsp;Live Effects&nbsp;in Xara Xtreme. <strong><a title=\"\" target=\"_top\" href=\"/products/xtreme/plugins\">Click here</a></strong> for more information.','2009-05-21 16:15:26',1),(353,'FEATURE_LIVE_EFFECTS_KEYWORDS','US','live;live effects;photoshop;plugin;plug-ins;','2009-05-21 16:15:26',0),(354,'FEATURE_NAVIGATION_BUTTONS_NAME','US','Navigation buttons','2009-05-21 16:49:07',1),(355,'FEATURE_NAVIGATION_BUTTONS_SHORT','US','With Xara Xtreme you can create standalone buttons or fully functional navigation bars within minutes. ','2009-05-21 16:49:07',1),(356,'FEATURE_NAVIGATION_BUTTONS_LONG','US','Buttons and navigation bars are an <strong>essential</strong> part of most web sites, but making them can be a time-consuming and frustrating experience. <br>\r\n<br>Xara Xtreme allows you to create standalone buttons or fully functional navigation bars within <strong>minutes</strong>. You can also create rollover buttons which change as you <strong>interact</strong> with them - and Xara Xtreme will write&nbsp;<strong>all the code</strong>&nbsp;for you.','2009-05-21 16:49:07',1),(357,'FEATURE_NAVIGATION_BUTTONS_KEYWORDS','US','web;button;navigation;navbar;','2009-05-21 16:49:07',0),(358,'FEATURE_FLASH_EXPORT_NAME','US','Flash export (.swf)','2008-03-20 15:12:45',1),(359,'FEATURE_FLASH_EXPORT_SHORT','US','Any image you make in Xara Xtreme can be exported in .swf format, which can then be imported into Flash. ','2008-03-20 15:12:45',1),(360,'FEATURE_FLASH_EXPORT_LONG','US','<p>Flash by Adobe has become a standard for vector graphic animations on the web. But, as web multimedia designers know, it\'s not the best tool for actually creating graphics.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />Any static&nbsp;image you create in Xara Xtreme can be <strong>exported in .swf format,</strong> which can then be imported into a Flash movie and animated. Because the graphic is in the Flash format, it <strong>remains</strong> <strong>scalable</strong>, so you can resize it and manipulate it within Flash without losing any quality.</p>\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme also has its own quick and easy <strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=89\">Flash animation</a></strong> feature.</p>','2008-03-20 15:12:45',1),(361,'FEATURE_FLASH_EXPORT_KEYWORDS','US','swf;flash','2008-03-20 15:12:45',0),(362,'FEATURE_GIF_ANIMATION_NAME','US','GIF Animation','2009-11-05 15:21:04',1),(363,'FEATURE_GIF_ANIMATION_SHORT','US','Animated gifs are still a common form of animation on the web and they are easy to create in Xtreme.','2009-11-05 15:21:04',1),(364,'FEATURE_GIF_ANIMATION_LONG','US','Animated gifs are still a common form of animation used on the web. Used for <strong>banner</strong> advertisements, spinning <strong>buttons</strong> and <strong>character</strong> animation, animated gifs will be around for a long time yet. <br>\r\n<br>The Xara Xtreme <strong>Frame Gallery</strong> allows you to create animations one frame at a time. It gives you <strong>complete control</strong> over every aspect of the animation from pauses between frames to the transparency of objects. <br>\r\n<br>When exporting, Xara Xtreme is able to fully optimize animated gifs so they have as small a file size as possible, meaning you can create <strong>eye-catching</strong> animations without hindering the performance of your site.','2009-11-05 15:21:04',1),(365,'FEATURE_GIF_ANIMATION_KEYWORDS','US','gif;animated;animation;web','2009-11-05 15:21:04',1),(366,'FEATURE_DREAMWEAVER_INTEGRATION_NAME','US','Dreamweaver integration','2008-03-20 15:13:47',1),(367,'FEATURE_DREAMWEAVER_INTEGRATION_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has a special option when exporting an image in a web format (gif, jpeg or png) which saves some extra information used by Dreamweaver, along with the graphic.','2008-03-20 15:13:47',1),(368,'FEATURE_DREAMWEAVER_INTEGRATION_LONG','US','Adobe\'s Dreamweaver is one of the leading web design packages and is used by designers across the world to create stunning web pages. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme has a <strong>special option</strong> when <strong>exporting</strong> an image in a web format (gif, jpeg or png) which saves some <strong>extra</strong> information used by Dreamweaver, along with the graphic. Then, when you\'re making a web page in Dreamweaver, you can <strong>insert</strong> the graphic as normal, but if you want to <strong>edit</strong> it at any point, just click on the image and Xara Xtreme will automatically load up with the graphic open. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Note</strong>: only works with Dreamweaver 3 or higher.','2008-03-20 15:13:47',1),(369,'FEATURE_DREAMWEAVER_INTEGRATION_KEYWORDS','US','dreamweaver;web;','2008-03-20 15:13:47',0),(370,'FEATURE_HEXADECIMAL_RGB_WEB_COLOR_NAME','US','Hexadecimal RGB web color','2008-03-20 15:14:14',1),(371,'FEATURE_HEXADECIMAL_RGB_WEB_COLOR_SHORT','US','Being able to select colors based on their hexadecimal value is vital for web designers. That way you can match your graphics with colors from the standard web safe color palette, that you use on your web page. ','2008-03-20 15:14:14',1),(372,'FEATURE_HEXADECIMAL_RGB_WEB_COLOR_LONG','US','Being able to select colors based on their hexadecimal value is <strong>vital</strong> for web designers. That way you can <strong>match</strong> your graphics with colors from the standard <strong>web safe color palette</strong>, that you use on your web page. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Often</strong> a designer will want to match a graphic color with the background color placed in a cell of a table for example. As HTML uses hexadecimal values (eg. #CCCCFF) to represent colors, it is <strong>extremely useful</strong> to be able to specify these colors within a drawing package. <br />\r\n<br />Especially for web designers, Xara Xtreme has a Hexadecimal RGB Web Color option which allows just this.','2008-03-20 15:14:14',1),(373,'FEATURE_HEXADECIMAL_RGB_WEB_COLOR_KEYWORDS','US','hex;hexadecimal;web;rgb;','2008-03-20 15:14:14',0),(374,'FEATURE_IMAGE_SLICING_NAME','US','Image slicing','2008-03-20 15:14:44',1),(375,'FEATURE_IMAGE_SLICING_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme not only slices and saves images for you, it also writes all the necessary HTML too, so you can just copy it into your web page. ','2008-03-20 15:14:44',1),(376,'FEATURE_IMAGE_SLICING_LONG','US','Large, complex graphics for web pages can produce <strong>large</strong> files, which take a <strong>long time to download</strong> over the Internet. <br />\r\n<br />However, often these large graphics contain areas of <strong>flat color</strong> or <strong>little detail</strong>. To reduce the amount of data to download you can \'<strong>slice</strong>\' the image into <strong>sections</strong>, which can be download <strong>separately</strong>. <br />\r\n<br />The advantage is that areas of flat color/little detail can be saved at a <strong>lower quality</strong> (eg. as a 2-color GIF) than complex areas, which can be saved at a <strong>higher resolution</strong>. The 2-color GIF file takes <strong>less time</strong> to download, but it means you can still have high detail areas within your image. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme not only slices and saves the images for you, it also <strong>writes</strong> all the necessary <strong>HTML</strong> too, so you can just copy it into your web page.','2008-03-20 15:14:44',1),(377,'FEATURE_IMAGE_SLICING_KEYWORDS','US','web;slice;slicing;','2008-03-20 15:14:44',0),(378,'FEATURE_IMAGE_MAPS_NAME','US','Image maps','2008-03-20 15:17:07',1),(379,'FEATURE_IMAGE_MAPS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme allows you to assign a web address to any object in a document. You can then export the complete image along with the necessary HTML required to make the image map work. ','2008-03-20 15:17:07',1),(380,'FEATURE_IMAGE_MAPS_LONG','US','Image maps are used in web pages to create <strong>clickable areas</strong> or <strong>hotspots</strong> on a graphic. For example, if you had a map of the United Kingdom - as shown in the example - you can use an image map with a hotspot over each country. <br />\r\n<br />Xara Xtreme allows you to <strong>assign a web address</strong> to any object in a document. You can then <strong>export</strong> the complete image along with the necessary HTML required to make the image map work. <br />\r\n<br />When assigning a web address to an object you have the option to make the hotspot fit the object exactly or roughly outline the area with a rectangle which can produce much less code than a complex shape. <br />\r\n<br />You also get the option to select where the link should point to - to a new window, the current frame, the parent frame and so on.','2008-03-20 15:17:07',1),(381,'FEATURE_IMAGE_MAPS_KEYWORDS','US','image;map;maps;web;','2008-03-20 15:17:07',0),(382,'FEATURE_EXPORTING_-_OPTIMIZING_NAME','US','Exporting and optimizing','2008-03-20 15:18:02',1),(383,'FEATURE_EXPORTING_-_OPTIMIZING_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme has fantastic built-in optimization for web graphics, and also allows you to take complete control of color palettes yourself.','2008-03-20 15:18:02',1),(384,'FEATURE_EXPORTING_-_OPTIMIZING_LONG','US','Optimization of web graphics is an <strong>essential</strong> factor if you want to keep <strong>fast download times</strong> for your web pages. <br />\r\n<br />In order to make graphics have the smallest file size possible, yet still look good, it is often necessary to optimize them. Xara Xtreme has <strong>fantastic</strong> built-in optimization for web graphics, and also allows you to take <strong>complete control</strong> of color palettes yourself. <br />\r\n<br />This means that you can choose the <strong>exact</strong> settings you want, including: color depth, dithering and transparency. You can also <strong>lock</strong> specific colors to make sure they are retained within the image. You can <strong>preview</strong> every change you make so you can see what the result will be before committing yourself and in the Export Dialog you can compare different export options so you know which one is best.','2008-03-20 15:18:02',1),(385,'FEATURE_EXPORTING_-_OPTIMIZING_KEYWORDS','US','export;exporting;optimization;optimize;optimize;optimisation;','2008-03-20 15:18:02',0),(386,'FEATURE_LINKED_STRETCHING_NAME','US','Linked stretching','2009-05-21 17:07:23',1),(387,'FEATURE_LINKED_STRETCHING_SHORT','US','Linked stretching is the process of setting one object to stretch another object - most typically setting the button text to stretch a button graphic, so when you make the button text longer the button graphic stretches to match.','2009-05-21 17:07:23',1),(388,'FEATURE_LINKED_STRETCHING_LONG','US','Linked stretching is the process of using named objects to stretch or <strong>extend</strong> other named objects. <br>\r\n<br>One of the most typical uses for Linked Stretching is when making a <strong>button with text</strong> on it, typically for a navigation bar on a web page. It means that when you change the text, the button <strong>automatically stretches</strong> so the text fits on it perfectly.','2009-05-21 17:07:23',1),(389,'FEATURE_LINKED_STRETCHING_KEYWORDS','US','linked stretching;buttons;web;','2009-05-21 17:07:23',0),(390,'FEATURE_CAT_COMPATIBILITY','US','Compatibility &amp; Workflow','2009-05-22 12:32:13',1),(391,'FEATURE_CAT_PRODINTERFACE','US','Productivity &amp; Interface ','2009-05-22 12:22:25',1),(392,'FEATURE_CAT_PHOTOHANDLING','US','Revolutionary Photo Handling','2008-09-02 19:11:02',1),(393,'FEATURE_CAT_TOOLS','US','Creative Tools','2009-05-22 12:20:14',1),(394,'FEATURE_CAT_TOP10','US','Top 10 cool things about Xtreme','2008-02-11 10:37:31',1),(398,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_THE_WEB','US','The new features in Xtreme V5 make it a first class web authoring tool in its own right','2009-05-22 12:32:16',1),(399,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_GENERAL','US','','2009-02-02 17:01:36',1),(400,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_PHOTO','US','','2008-02-12 16:53:39',1),(401,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_ILLUSTRATION','US','','2008-02-12 16:53:40',1),(402,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WEB','US','','2008-02-12 16:53:43',1),(403,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_XTREME','US','','2008-02-12 16:53:45',1),(404,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_XTREMEPRO','US','','2008-02-13 08:53:40',1),(405,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_COMPATIBILITY','US','Xara Xtreme is used by many different types of customer in a spectacular range of uses - for designs combining drawings, text and photos, for print and the web - so we understand how important it is to offer compatibility with other products and users.','2009-05-22 12:32:13',1),(406,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_PRODINTERFACE','US','Xara Xtreme is famous for its speed and unrivalled ease of use, making it not just a highly productive tool, but a pleasure to be creative.','2009-05-22 12:22:25',1),(407,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_PHOTOHANDLING','US','Xara Xtreme photo handling beats other graphics programs on many fronts','2008-09-02 19:11:02',1),(408,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_TOOLS','US','Xara Xtreme offers all the tools that a creative designer could need','2009-05-22 12:20:14',1),(409,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_TOP10','US','','2008-02-11 10:37:31',1),(415,'FEATURE_COMPATIBILITY_LONG','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1742,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_SHORT','DE','Xara Xtremes einzigartige Weise, Fotos zu bearbeiten und zu speichern (verlustfreie, vektor-basierte Fotobearbeitung, kombiniert mit dem Einbetten des Original-JPEGs) führt dazu, dass Dateien, die Fotos enthalten zwischen 3 und 100 mal kleiner als mit anderen Programmen sind.','2008-06-04 17:07:53',1),(1743,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_LONG','DE','<p>Xara Xtreme bettet Ihr Original-JPEG in die Xara-Datei ein, was Ihnen viel Speicherplatz spart. Ein 5-Megapixel JPEG-Foto von einer Digitalkamera wäre in anderen Grafikprogrammen normalerweise über 20 Megabyte groß. Sobald Sie zwei oder drei solcher Bilder in Ihrem Dokument haben oder Kopien eines Bildes editieren, haben Sie schnell eine Datei, die 60 Megabyte groß ist. Xara Xtreme Dateien sind nur ein Zehntel so groß.</p>\r\n<p>Hinzu kommt die ohnehin erstaunliche Kompaktheit von Xara Xtreme Dateien, so dass Sie diese viel schneller speichern und laden können. Das direkte Neuzeichnen macht das Arbeiten mit Fotos zu einer Freude, selbst wenn diese von modernen, sehr hochauflösenden Kameras stammen. Dies ist zusätzlich praktisch, wenn Sie Ihre Dateien mit anderen Xara Xtreme Anwendern per E-Mail austauschen.&nbsp;</p>','2008-06-13 16:15:21',1),(1744,'FEATURE_FILE_SIZE_KEYWORDS','DE','...','2008-01-01 00:00:00',1),(1745,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_SHORT','DE','MAGIX Xtreme Foto Designer ist ein Foto-Editor, der im Lieferumfang von Xtreme enthalten ist.','2008-06-04 17:14:18',1),(1746,'FEATURE_MAGIX_XTREME_PHOTO_DESIGNER_LONG','DE','<p>Der MAGIX Xtreme Foto Designer ist ein Foto-Editor, der mit Xtreme mitgeliefert wird. In der aktuellen Version von Xtreme ist es möglich, den Foto Designer oder jeden anderen externen Foto-Editor auszuwählen. Hier finden Sie einige kurze Details über den MAGIX Xtreme Foto Designer von der MAGIX Homepage:</p>\r\n<p>Fügen Sie Ihren Bildern neuen Glanz hinzu oder teleportieren Sie sich aus Ihrem Garten in die Südsee mit der Foto-Montage-Funktion. Machen Sie kunstvolle Ölgemälde aus Ihren Bildern und gestalten Sie Ihr Wohnzimmer um zu Ihrer ganz persönlichen Galerie. All Ihre kreativen Ideen können Sie mit wenigen Mausklicks zur Wirklichkeit werden lassen. Mit dem MAGIX Xtreme Foto Designer machen Sie sehr einfach das Beste aus Ihren Bildern, eben weil professionelle Ergebnisse so einfach sind.&nbsp; </p>\r\n<h1>Ihre Vorteile:</h1>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" bordercolor=\"#000000\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"4\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"src=/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/det_bearb_Kopie.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"width=\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\"><br />\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"5\">\r\n<p><strong>Professionelle Bearbeitung<br />\r\n</strong>Panorama-Bilder, Foto-Montagen, Beschneiden, Airbrush...</p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"src=/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/emo_usecase-art.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"width=\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\"><br />\r\n</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"5\">\r\n<p><strong>Künstlerische Verfremdung<br />\r\n</strong>Innovative Kunsteffekte für Ölgemälde, Karikaturen, Mosaike und Stiftzeichnungen...</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"height=\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"src=/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/bildimbild_1.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"width=0\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"5\">\r\n<p><strong>Bild-im-Bild<br />\r\n</strong>Realistische Foto-Montagen,<br />\r\nTextfelder, die im Hintergrund verschwinden...</p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"src=/img/us/products/xtreme/features/magixphoto/bildschirm.jpg\" border=\"0\" height=\"width=\" /></p></td>\r\n<td width=\"\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></td>\r\n<td valign=\"