P','US','Buy Xara Xtreme here. Xara Xtreme offers an unbeatably fast and easy way to create graphics, combining drawings, photos and text','2008-04-01 10:51:09',1),(698,'PAGE_TITLE_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_BUY','US','Buy Xara Xtreme','2009-05-15 18:57:54',1),(699,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_BUY','US','xara, xara xtreme, graphics software, drawing software, illustration software, vector graphics, buy xara, purchase xara, xara shop','2009-05-15 18:57:54',1),(700,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_BUY','US','Buy Xara Xtreme here. Xara Xtreme offers an unbeatably fast and easy way to create graphics, combining drawings, photos and text','2009-05-15 18:57:54',1),(702,'HIGHLIGHT_UK','UK','countryselect2over','2008-02-15 16:30:10',0),(703,'HIGHLIGHT_UK','US','countryselect2','2008-02-15 16:30:01',0),(704,'HIGHLIGHT_UK','DE','countryselect2','2008-02-15 16:29:53',0),(705,'HIGHLIGHT_US','UK','countryselect2','2008-02-15 16:32:34',0),(706,'HIGHLIGHT_DE','UK','countryselect2','2008-02-15 16:30:42',0),(2234,'BUTTON_UPGRADING','US','UPGRADING/DISCOUNTS','2008-05-08 15:52:09',1),(707,'FEATURE_FLASH_COMPONENT_1_NAME','US','First new feature','2008-02-19 19:00:25',1),(708,'FEATURE_FLASH_COMPONENT_1_SHORT','US','Some text here...','2008-02-19 19:00:25',1),(709,'FEATURE_FLASH_COMPONENT_1_LONG','US','','2008-02-19 19:00:25',1),(710,'FEATURE_FLASH_COMPONENT_1_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-02-19 19:00:25',0),(731,'FEATURE_MULTI-CORE_PROCESSORS_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme has always had by far the highest performing graphics rendering engine, up to ten times faster than Adobe Illustrator.&nbsp;V4 introduced&nbsp;support for multi-core processors in Xara Xtreme Pro&nbsp;making it&nbsp;even faster than before! Tests show approximate speed gains of 40% for a dual core processor with large screen images, and greater gains with more cores. Large full screen photos can render up to 75% faster on a dual core processor.</p>','2009-05-20 18:56:53',1),(732,'FEATURE_MULTI-CORE_PROCESSORS_KEYWORDS','US','multi-core;dual core;processor;speed','2009-05-20 18:56:53',0),(712,'SWF_ZOOM','US','<div id=\"FEATURE_ZOOM2_MEDIA\">Please install Flash&reg; and turn on Javascript.</div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"> \r\n// <![CDATA[ \r\nvar so = new SWFObject(\"/flash/us/products/xtreme/features/zoom_anim.swf\", \"ZOOM\", \"315\", \"170\", \"8\"); \r\nso.addParam(\"wmode\", \"transparent\"); \r\nso.write(\"FEATURE_ZOOM2_MEDIA\"); \r\n// ]]> \r\n</script>','2008-03-07 17:43:27',0),(973,'FEATURE_CAT_WHATSNEWXTREME','US','What\'s New in Xtreme 4','2008-03-07 18:47:27',1),(713,'FEATURE_HTML_WEBSITE_CREATION_XTREME_NAME','US','HTML Website Creation','2009-11-05 16:50:39',1),(714,'FEATURE_HTML_WEBSITE_CREATION_XTREME_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme includes a complete \'website creation\' feature that enables you to design multi-page websites with ease,  including mouseover and pop-up effects, animations and widgets. One click preview and ftp upload included. It\'s the world\'s most advanced WYSIWYG web page layout - and with no HTML skills required!','2009-11-05 16:50:39',1),(715,'FEATURE_HTML_WEBSITE_CREATION_XTREME_LONG','US','<p>With Xara Xtreme you can easily create HTML web pages and even multi-page websites, in a totally WYSIWYG fashion -&nbsp;absolutely no HTML skills required.</p>\r\n<p>The advantage of using Xtreme to create web pages&nbsp;is that you get <strong>complete freedom to position items anywhere on the page</strong>, to include as many graphics as you like (even semi-transparent graphics) with text - even rotated text - wherever you like! And Xara Xtreme will <strong>create all the HTML for you</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Xtreme can create <strong>multi-page websites</strong> using the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=25\"><strong>multi-page document</strong></a> feature. </p>\r\n<p><strong>V5 brings significant enhancements</strong> in this area, including single click website preview, ftp upload, an improved ability to include third party \'<a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=308\">widgets</a>\', enhanced mouseover and pop-up effects and improved text flow around photos and irregular text margins. Xtreme is&nbsp;now a&nbsp;first class web authoring tool in its own right.</p>\r\n<p>An as you would expect, Xtreme produces cross browser, cross platform compatible, fully standards compliant (X)HTML.</p>\r\n<p>The Xtreme CD also includes a selection of <strong>professionally designed HTML website </strong><a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=22\"><strong>templates</strong></a>.</p>\r\n<p>You can see an example site created in Xara Xtreme&nbsp;at <a title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://xtreme.xara.com/index.htm\">xtreme.xara.com</a>&nbsp;- it\'s also an introduction to the web features.</p>','2009-11-05 16:50:39',1),(716,'FEATURE_HTML_WEBSITE_CREATION_XTREME_KEYWORDS','US','HTML;web;export','2009-11-05 16:50:39',1),(730,'FEATURE_MULTI-CORE_PROCESSORS_SHORT','US','Multi-core processor support in Xara Xtreme Pro, making the world\'s fastest graphics software even faster!','2009-05-20 18:56:53',1),(717,'FEATURE_PHOTO_PANORAMAS_NAME','US','Photo Panoramas','2009-05-20 18:58:34',1),(718,'FEATURE_PHOTO_PANORAMAS_SHORT','US','Perhaps the easiest to use panorama maker. Drop a series of photos on the page, click one button and you\'ll get a perfect, seamless joined panoramic image.','2009-05-20 18:58:34',1),(719,'FEATURE_PHOTO_PANORAMAS_LONG','US','<p>Using&nbsp;the integrated photo tool in Xara Xtreme you can easily create <strong>panorama pictures.</strong> The integrated panorama picture assistant helps you seamlessly attach the individual pictures of your panorama-to-be to one another. Simply import your pictures, optimize the picture transitions, and you\'re done. In just a few clicks you can turn your individual pictures into tailor-made panorama pictures. </p>','2009-05-20 18:58:34',1),(720,'FEATURE_PHOTO_PANORAMAS_KEYWORDS','US','panorama;photo;photos','2009-05-20 18:58:34',0),(721,'FEATURE_ADOBE_PHOTOSHOP_PLUG-INS_NAME','US','Adobe Photoshop® Plug-ins','2009-05-21 16:09:14',1),(722,'FEATURE_ADOBE_PHOTOSHOP_PLUG-INS_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme supports Adobe Photoshop® plug-ins. There\'s already a huge range of such plug-ins available, both free and commercial, for creating a variety of effects that would take a lifetime to explore.\r\nIn addition the Live Effects tool, the most advanced of any available, enables you to apply these plug-ins to photos and vector shapes for a range of amazing visual effects.\r\nXtreme includes more than 35 built-in Live Effects.','2009-05-21 16:09:14',1),(723,'FEATURE_ADOBE_PHOTOSHOP_PLUG-INS_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme supports Adobe Photoshop plug-ins.&nbsp;There\'s already a huge range of such plug-ins available,&nbsp;both free and commercial, for creating a variety of effects that would take a lifetime to explore - metallic effects, color and image distortions, glows, water ripples, crumples&nbsp;etc etc. </p>\r\n<p>These plug-ins can be used with both bitmaps and vector drawn images - check out the <a title=\"\" href=\"/products/xtreme/features/feature?id=55\"><strong>Live Effects tool</strong></a><strong>.</strong></p>\r\n<p>We have bundled a selection of the best plug-ins&nbsp;with Xara Xtreme, including examples from Alien Skin, Redfield, AV Bros and Mehdi, plus more than 35 new plug-ins from MAGIX. <strong><a title=\"\" target=\"_top\" href=\"/products/xtreme/plugins\">Click here</a></strong> to view them.</p>','2009-05-21 16:09:14',1),(724,'FEATURE_ADOBE_PHOTOSHOP_PLUG-INS_KEYWORDS','US','photoshop;plugin;plug-in;','2009-05-21 16:09:14',0),(725,'FEATURE_HD_PHOTO_IMPORT_NAME','US','HD Photo import','2009-05-20 18:59:18',1),(726,'FEATURE_HD_PHOTO_IMPORT_SHORT','US','Xara Xtreme Pro can import the new HD Photo format, also known as Windows Media Photo.','2009-05-20 18:59:18',1),(727,'FEATURE_HD_PHOTO_IMPORT_LONG','US','<p>Xara Xtreme Pro imports the new HD Photo format, also known as Windows Media Photo. Files can be saved in this HD photo format by Adobe Photoshop CS2 and CS3 plus Microsoft Expression Design.</p>','2009-05-20 18:59:18',1),(728,'FEATURE_HD_PHOTO_IMPORT_KEYWORDS','US','photo hd;photo;photos;windows media photo;','2009-05-20 18:59:18',0),(729,'FEATURE_MULTI-CORE_PROCESSORS_NAME','US','Multi-core processors','2009-05-20 18:56:53',1),(733,'IMG_FEATURE_02_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/02.jpg','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(734,'IMG_FEATURE_02','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/02.jpg\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(735,'IMG_FEATURE_ANTIALIAS2_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/antialias2.gif','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(736,'IMG_FEATURE_ANTIALIAS2','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/antialias2.gif\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(737,'IMG_FEATURE_BEVEL2_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bevel2.gif','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(738,'IMG_FEATURE_BEVEL2','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bevel2.gif\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(739,'IMG_FEATURE_BITMAPHANDLE3_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bitmaphandle3.jpg','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(740,'IMG_FEATURE_BITMAPHANDLE3','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bitmaphandle3.jpg\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(741,'IMG_FEATURE_BITMAPTRACER_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bitmaptracer.jpg','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(742,'IMG_FEATURE_BITMAPTRACER','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/bitmaptracer.jpg\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(743,'IMG_FEATURE_BLEND_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/blend.gif','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(744,'IMG_FEATURE_BLEND','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/blend.gif\" />','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(745,'IMG_FEATURE_BOXGRAPHIC_URL','US','/img/us/products/xtreme/features/boxgraphic.jpg','2008-02-19 16:45:33',0),(746,'IMG_FEATURE_BOXGRAPHIC','US','<img src=\"/img/us/products/xtreme/features/boxgraphic.jpg\" />','2008-02-19