ve photo tool','2009-05-20 13:42:13',1),(991,'FEATURE_WN_PHOTO_TOOL_SHORT','US','','2009-05-20 13:42:13',1),(992,'FEATURE_WN_PHOTO_TOOL_LONG','US','<p>The new photo tool offers instantaneous editing for even huge photos. All operations are non-destructive, meaning the original image is not affected and all edits are object orientated and undoable. This also means edits like this take practically no file space and so allows ultra compact lossless files. The features include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ultra-fast, live &amp; interactive Enhance (brightness, sharpness, saturation etc) </li>\r\n<li>Levels (histogram, color correction and more) </li>\r\n<li>Interactive crop. Again this is non-destructive so you can adjust or un-crop images at any time. </li>\r\n<li>An automatic panorama maker photo-stitching feature.</li></ul>','2009-05-20 13:42:13',1),(993,'FEATURE_WN_PHOTO_TOOL_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-05-20 13:42:13',0),(994,'FEATURE_WN_3D_EXTRUDE_NAME','US','The world\'s fastest, highest quality vector 3D extrude tool','2008-03-12 11:38:16',1),(995,'FEATURE_WN_3D_EXTRUDE_SHORT','US','','2008-03-12 11:38:16',1),(996,'FEATURE_WN_3D_EXTRUDE_LONG','US','<p>Xara3D has been integrated so you can now extrude objects in 3D. This provides industry leading speed, usability and quality of 3D rendering compared with any other drawing package. It provides live on-canvas 3D dragging and extrude, 3 colored lights than can be dragged around in real-time, and Xara\'s renowned high quality 3D rendering.</p>','2008-03-12 11:38:16',1),(997,'FEATURE_WN_3D_EXTRUDE_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-12 11:38:16',0),(998,'FEATURE_WN_TEXT_TOOL_NAME','US','Major text tool improvements, including real-time \'liquid\' text flow around shapes','2008-03-27 13:18:12',1),(999,'FEATURE_WN_TEXT_TOOL_SHORT','US','','2008-03-27 13:18:12',1),(1024,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_STD_LONG','US','<ul>\r\n<li>A new option for marquee select provides an Adobe-like selection so that any objects that the marquee rectangle touches are selected. An alternative option selects only those objects entirely inside the marquee rectangle. </li>\r\n<li>Selection has been made live - objects are selected as you drag, rather than only when you let go. This mkes it easier to know whether objects are or are not selected as you drag, rather than waiting until you let go of the mouse.</li></ul>','2008-03-10 13:09:58',1),(1000,'FEATURE_WN_TEXT_TOOL_LONG','US','<ul>\r\n<li>A new text repel feature allows text to flow around shapes and photos. As you\'d expect from Xara this provides super-fast text re-formatting allowing live and interactive flow of text as you drag the text objects </li>\r\n<li>New live reformatting while resizing text columns and frames </li>\r\n<li>Text underline</li></ul>','2008-03-27 13:18:12',1),(1001,'FEATURE_WN_TEXT_TOOL_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-27 13:18:12',0),(1002,'FEATURE_WN_HTML_EXPORT_NAME','US','A new \'website creation\' feature. Build complete multi-page websites, with the world\'s most advanced WYSIWYG page layout controls','2008-03-10 13:06:39',1),(1003,'FEATURE_WN_HTML_EXPORT_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:06:39',1),(1023,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_STD_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:09:58',1),(1004,'FEATURE_WN_HTML_EXPORT_LONG','US','<p>Many professional graphic designers already use Xara as their primary web graphics tool. Now it can save complete HTML web pages (using XHTML and CSS standards) and using layers it is easy to add mouseover effects and even add pop-ups.&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p>The advantage of using Xtreme to create web pages is that you get almost complete freedom to position graphics and text anywhere on the page – including semi-transparent graphics and even rotated text - things which would be difficult or impossible with normal web authoring tools.&nbsp; Plus the multi-page feature can be used to create complete multi-page websites. And Xtreme creates all the HTML for you.</p>','2008-03-10 13:06:39',1),(1005,'FEATURE_WN_HTML_EXPORT_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:06:39',0),(1006,'FEATURE_WN_RENDERING_NAME','US','New super-high quality vector and photo rendering','2008-03-10 13:07:03',1),(1007,'FEATURE_WN_RENDERING_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:07:03',1),(1022,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_STD_NAME','US','Flexible new Selector tool options','2008-03-10 13:09:58',1),(1008,'FEATURE_WN_RENDERING_LONG','US','<p>A new simplified Quality Control provides five quality steps: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Outline only. This is now fully anti-aliased for higher quality screen display </li>\r\n<li>Outline with blend steps </li>\r\n<li>Full color (no anti-aliasing) </li>\r\n<li>High Quality (full anti-aliasing. Same as previous top quality. Provides image smoothing) </li>\r\n<li>Very high quality (new higher quality, industry best anti-aliasing. New bi-cubic photo display considerably improves the quality of scaled down photos).<br />\r\n</li></ul>','2008-03-10 13:07:03',1),(1009,'FEATURE_WN_RENDERING_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:07:03',0),(1010,'FEATURE_WN_MULTI-PROCESSORS_NAME','US','Support for multi-core processors - the world\'s fastest graphics program is now even faster!','2008-03-10 15:10:02',1),(1011,'FEATURE_WN_MULTI-PROCESSORS_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 15:10:02',1),(1054,'FEATURE_WN_ZOOM_OUT_ON_IMAGE_NAME','US','Zoom out now retains the image in the center of the screen even down to small zoom','2008-03-10 16:00:32',1),(1012,'FEATURE_WN_MULTI-PROCESSORS_LONG','US','<p>Xara always had by far the highest performing graphics rendering engine, up to ten times faster than Adobe. Now with support for multi-core processors it\'s even faster. Tests show approximate speed gains of 40% for dual core processors with large screen images and greater gains with more cores. Large full screen photos can render up to 75% faster on a dual core processor.</p>','2008-03-10 15:10:02',1),(1013,'FEATURE_WN_MULTI-PROCESSORS_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 15:10:02',0),(1014,'FEATURE_WN_COLOR_NAME','US','Improved color picking and editing including an enhanced eye dropper color picker on the color line','2008-03-10 13:06:56',1),(1015,'FEATURE_WN_COLOR_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:06:56',1),(1016,'FEATURE_WN_COLOR_LONG','US','<ul>\r\n<li>You can now use the eye-dropper color picker directly without having the color editor on screen. </li>\r\n<li>The Color line now indicates the color under the eye-dropper as you\'re dragging around, highlighting the named or palette color. </li>\r\n<li>There are new live color values shown next to the eye-dropper as you move over objects, showing not just the RGB color but the correct named color and color model of the object under the pointer. e.g. whether it\'s a spot, Pantone, CMYK or RGB color, and its value. </li>\r\n<li>The current fill and line colors are now indicated on the color line even if they are palette colors, not just named colors.&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>The Name Gallery now shows used palette colors and edited colors, not just named colors.</li></ul>','2008-03-10 13:06:56',1),(1017,'FEATURE_WN_COLOR_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:06:56',0),(1018,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_PRO_NAME','US','Flexible new Selector tool options','2008-03-10 13:05:40',1),(1019,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_PRO_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:05:40',1),(1020,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_PRO_LONG','US','<ul>\r\n<li>A new \'scribble select\' feature allows you to select objects by just drawing a freehand line over the page - all objects that the line touches are added to the selection. </li>\r\n<li>A new option for marquee select provides an Adobe-like selection so that any objects that the marquee rectangle touches are selected. An alternative option selects only those objects entirely inside the marquee rectangle. </li>\r\n<li>Selection has been made live - objects are selected as you drag, rather than only when you let go. This mkes it easier to know whether objects are or are not selected as you drag, rather than waiting until you let go of the mouse.</li></ul>','2008-03-10 13:05:40',1),(1021,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_PRO_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:05:40',0),(1025,'FEATURE_WN_SELECTOR_TOOL_-_STD_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:09:58',0),(1026,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_STD_NAME','US','New and improved import and export of industry standard graphics formats','2008-03-10 13:18:30',1),(1027,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_STD_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:18:30',1),(1028,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_STD_LONG','US','<p>This includes: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improved PDF import</li></ul>','2008-03-10 13:18:30',1),(1034,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_UNICODE_NAME','US','Improved international font and text (Unicode) handling','2008-04-01 20:33:29',1),(1035,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_UNICODE_SHORT','US','','2008-04-01 20:33:29',1),(1036,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_UNICODE_LONG','US','<p>Improved Unicode support for foreign language alphabets, such as Chinese.</p>','2008-04-01 20:33:29',1),(1029,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_STD_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:18:30',0),(1030,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_PRO_NAME','US','New and improved import and export of industry standard graphics formats','2008-10-07 17:45:07',1),(900,'FEATURE_LIQUID_TEXT_FLOW_NAME','US','Liquid Text Flow','2009-05-22 12:38:36',1),(901,'FEATURE_LIQUID_TEXT_FLOW_SHORT','US','Unbeatably fast and flexible text handling with top quality rendering, now offering real-time \'liquid\' text flow around shapes. Plus a new font menu including Live Preview, for instant preview of fonts on the page.','2009-05-22 12:38:36',1),(902,'FEATURE_LIQUID_TEXT_FLOW_LONG','US','','2009-05-22 12:38:36',1),(903,'FEATURE_LIQUID_TEXT_FLOW_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-05-22 12:38:36',0),(904,'PAGE_TITLE_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_FEATURES_FEATURE','US','Xara Xtreme Features','2009-05-27 18:17:14',1),(905,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_FEATURES_FEATURE','US','Xara, xara xtreme, corelxara, graphics, software, vector graphics, graphics software, drawing software, 3d, illustration software, 3D software, web design, web graphics, animation, animated GIF, GIF, Flash, Flash design, flash animation, image, clipart, shareware, download,','2009-05-27 18:17:14',1),(906,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_FEATURES_FEATURE','US','Xara Xtreme offers an unbeatably fast and easy way to create graphics, combining drawings, photos and text','2009-05-27 18:17:14',1),(907,'PAGE_TITLE_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_TUTORIALS-DEMOS','US','Xara Xtreme Tutorials','2009-05-18 18:16:24',1),(908,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_TUTORIALS-DEMOS','US','xara, xara xtreme, graphics software, drawing software, illustration software, vector graphics, tutorials, xara tutorial, xara demo','2009-05-18 18:16:24',1),(909,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_XARA_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_TUTORIALS-DEMOS','US','Check out the Xara Xtreme tutorials. Xara Xtreme offers an unbeatably fast and easy way to create graphics, combining drawings, photos and text','2009-05-18 18:16:24',1),(910,'PAGE_TITLE_AL__GALLERY','US','The Xara Gallery','2008-02-25 18:05:53',1),(911,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__GALLERY','US','xara, xara xtreme, xara gallery, xara graphics, xara design, graphics software, drawing software, illustration software, vector graphics, xara art, ','2008-02-25 18:05:53',1),(912,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__GALLERY','US','Check out the work of Xara artists worldwide','2008-02-25 18:05:53',1),(913,'PAGE_TITLE_AL__GALLERY_ARTIST','US','The Xara Gallery','2008-02-25 18:06:16',1),(914,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__GALLERY_ARTIST','US','xara, xara xtreme, xara gallery, xara graphics, xara design, graphics software, drawing software, illustration software, vector graphics, xara art, ','2008-02-25 18:06:16',1),(915,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__GALLERY_ARTIST','US','Check out the work of Xara artists worldwide','2008-02-25 18:06:16',1),(1031,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_PRO_SHORT','US','','2008-10-07 17:45:07',1),(1032,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_PRO_LONG','US','<p>This includes: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improved PDF import </li>\r\n<li>New XPS import (beta)</li>\r\n<li>New JPEG 2000 import / export and some other minor formats </li>\r\n<li>HD Photo import. This is a new high quality photo format from Microsoft, also known as Windows Media Photo. </li></ul>','2008-10-07 17:45:07',1),(1033,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_-_EXPORT_-_PRO_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-10-07 17:45:07',0),(1038,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_MENU_NAME','US','A new hierarchical Font menu with WYSIWYG font display','2008-04-01 20:24:31',1),(1039,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_MENU_SHORT','US','','2008-04-01 20:24:31',1),(1040,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_MENU_LONG','US','<p>Completely new WYSIWYG Font menu, now showing fonts grouped in families, showing full length font names and rendered in the corresponding font (high quality anti-aliased, compare with Word), so making it much easier to preview a font before selection. This is a hierarchical menu, so it\'s more compact and shows all variants of each family in a sub-menu.</p>','2008-04-01 20:24:31',1),(1041,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_MENU_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-04-01 20:24:31',0),(1037,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_UNICODE_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-04-01 20:33:29',0),(1042,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_PREVIEW_NAME','US','Live in-document font preview and live font size selection','2008-03-10 13:50:13',1),(1043,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_PREVIEW_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 13:50:13',1),(1044,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_PREVIEW_LONG','US','<p>Live Font Preview. As you traverse the font menu, the selected text in the document is updated. Similarly there is now a live font size preview, and a new interactive font size pop-up slider for fast, live, fine grained text size control.</p>','2008-03-10 13:50:13',1),(1045,'FEATURE_WN_FONT_PREVIEW_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 13:50:13',0),(1046,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_STD_NAME','US','A completely new automatic panorama photo stitching feature','2008-03-25 18:04:04',1),(1047,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_STD_SHORT','US','','2008-03-25 18:04:04',1),(1048,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_STD_LONG','US','<p>This is a new photo plug-in included in all copies of Xara Xtreme. It offers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Automatic stitching of photos to create a panorama </li>\r\n<li>Automatic detection of overlap and join positions </li>\r\n<li>Automatic calculation of focal length&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>Adjustment of pictures to reduce fish-eye or focal length distortions </li>\r\n<li>Seamless blending to remove dramatic color changes in the sky, for example. </li></ul>\r\n<p>The best bit is that it\'s utterly simple to use. Import your pictures, position them in the correct left to right order and then just click the Panorama button for them to be automatically stitched together.</p>','2008-03-25 18:04:04',1),(1049,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_STD_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-25 18:04:04',0),(1050,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_PRO_NAME','US','A free copy of Pan Studio, an advanced version of the panorama photo stitching feature','2008-04-01 14:01:23',1),(1051,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_PRO_SHORT','US','','2008-04-01 14:01:23',1),(1052,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_PRO_LONG','US','<p>This is a new photo plug-in included in all copies of Xara Xtreme. It offers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Automatic stitching of photos to create a panorama </li>\r\n<li>Automatic detection of overlap and join positions </li>\r\n<li>Automatic calculation of focal length </li>\r\n<li>Adjustment of pictures to reduce fish-eye or focal length distortions </li>\r\n<li>Seamless blending to remove dramatic color changes in the sky, for example.</li></ul>The best bit is that it\'s utterly simple to use. Import your pictures, position them in the correct left to right order and then just click the Panorama button for them to be automatically stitched together.\r\n<p>Xara Xtreme Pro includes a more advanced version of the same feature, called Panorama Studio (owners of the standard version of Xara Xtreme can upgrade separately). Pan Studio offers:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The ability to stitch together any number of images </li>\r\n<li>Advanced control over cropping, sharpening and enhancing of the resulting stitched image </li>\r\n<li>Create web based 360 degree panoramas, perfect for showing off your restaurant interior and that type of thing.</li></ul>','2008-04-01 14:01:23',1),(1053,'FEATURE_WN_PANORAMA_-_PRO_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-04-01 14:01:23',0),(1055,'FEATURE_WN_ZOOM_OUT_ON_IMAGE_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 16:00:32',1),(1056,'FEATURE_WN_ZOOM_OUT_ON_IMAGE_LONG','US','','2008-03-10 16:00:32',1),(1057,'FEATURE_WN_ZOOM_OUT_ON_IMAGE_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 16:00:32',0),(1058,'PAGE_TITLE_AL__CONTRIBUTE','US','Add your work to Xara.com','2008-03-10 17:07:21',1),(1059,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__CONTRIBUTE','US','xara,website','2008-03-10 17:07:21',1),(1060,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__CONTRIBUTE','US','The xara website','2008-03-10 17:07:21',1),(1061,'TITLE_CONTRIBUTE_PANEL','US','Add your work to Xara.com','2008-03-10 17:08:04',1),(1062,'DESC_CONTRIBUTE_PANEL','US','Thank you for requesting to add your work to our site. Please complete you details below, and then select the relevant tab to upload your work.','2008-03-10 17:12:59',1),(2247,'SHOWALLINFO','US','Show all info','2008-05-08 17:21:31',1),(1064,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__CONTRIBUTORDETAILS','US','xara,website','2008-03-10 17:15:17',1),(1065,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__CONTRIBUTORDETAILS','US','The xara website','2008-03-10 17:15:17',1),(1073,'USER_5_DESC','US','a \" b','2008-03-10 18:22:03',1),(1074,'USER_5_WEB','US','','2008-03-10 18:22:03',1),(1083,'FEATURE_WN_IMPORT_TO_NEW_PAGE_NAME','US','New \'import to new page\' option in the clipart gallery','2008-03-10 18:07:02',1),(1072,'USER_5_NAME','US','Jim','2008-03-10 18:22:03',1),(1076,'FEATURE_WN_MEGAPIXELS_SHORT','US','','2008-03-10 18:03:54',1),(1077,'FEATURE_WN_MEGAPIXELS_LONG','US','','2008-03-10 18:03:54',1),(1078,'FEATURE_WN_MEGAPIXELS_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-03-10 18:03:54',0),(1079,'FEATURE_WN_SINGLE_TILE_BITMAPS_NAME','US','Single tile bitmap fills now show transparent around the outside, in order to avoid edge aliasing effects (and it\'s also more compatible with Adobe clip regions).','2008-03-10 18:04:56',1),(1080,'FEATURE_WN_SINGLE_TIL