-09-01 16:21:05',0),(1122,'FEATURE_REV_PC_ADVISOR2_SHORT','US','','2008-09-01 16:21:05',0),(1123,'FEATURE_REV_PC_ADVISOR2_LONG','US','“Fast and inexpensive, Xara Xtreme Pro 4.0 is an excellent choice for print and web designers on a budget – or a deadline.”<br />\r\n<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.pcadvisor.co.uk/reviews/index.cfm?reviewid=2091\">Read the review</a>','2008-09-01 16:21:05',0),(1124,'FEATURE_REV_PC_ADVISOR2_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-09-01 16:21:05',0),(1125,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_ARTS_1_NAME','US','Computer Arts','2008-08-14 18:44:33',0),(1126,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_ARTS_1_SHORT','US','Recommended','2008-08-14 18:44:33',0),(1127,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_ARTS_1_LONG','US','\"If you\'ve never tried Xara, prepare to be astounded.\"<br />\r\n<br />\"The sheer simplicity of Xara Xtreme when working with gradient fills, transparency and shadows, not to mention gorgeous bevels and perfect anti-aliased output, make this program a joy to use.\"','2008-08-14 18:44:33',0),(1128,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_ARTS_1_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:44:33',0),(1129,'FEATURE_TEST_KEVIN_DICKINSON_NAME','US','Kevin Dickinson','2008-08-12 11:20:26',0),(1130,'FEATURE_TEST_KEVIN_DICKINSON_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:20:26',0),(1131,'FEATURE_TEST_KEVIN_DICKINSON_LONG','US','\"I would just like to take the time to congratulate all of the team at Xara for an outstanding product, superb support and brilliant marketing, advertising, sales and everything else. Your company excels at every point of contact and has done for many years. I have recently up (downgraded) to Vista and as a result have had to upgrade much of my software. You are a shining example of how things should be done with maximum efficiency and minimum hassle to the customer. I get the software immediately, I can pay easily, I get the CD in the post without fuss or problems, I get support by the bucketful in many different ways to suit me and to save hasseling you, unless I have to. Even registration is quick easy and hassle free.\"','2008-08-12 11:20:26',0),(1132,'FEATURE_TEST_KEVIN_DICKINSON_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:20:26',0),(1133,'FEATURE_TEST_ROGER_GELF-_NAME','US','Roger Gelfand','2009-08-05 18:01:44',0),(1134,'FEATURE_TEST_ROGER_GELF-_SHORT','US','I just wanted to tell you that I received Xara Xtreme Pro yesterday and that it is far above my expectations. Great to have the manuals as well as the disks. A great package.','2009-08-05 18:01:44',0),(1135,'FEATURE_TEST_ROGER_GELF-_LONG','US','\"I just wanted to tell you that I received Xara Xtreme Pro yesterday and that it is far above my expectations. Great to have the manuals as well as the disks. A great package.\"','2009-08-05 18:01:44',0),(1136,'FEATURE_TEST_ROGER_GELF-_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-05 18:01:44',0),(1137,'AWARD_PCADVISOR_GOLD','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/pcadvisor_gold.jpg\" />','2008-03-12 15:22:20',0),(1138,'REVIEWS-TESTIMONIALS_INTRO','US','Here\'s just a selection of the rave reviews from the press, and testimonials from some of our users about Xara Xtreme 4. We will be adding reviews on the brand new V5 as soon as they\'re in!','2009-05-20 18:50:22',1),(1139,'FEATURE_REV_DIGIT_NAME','US','Digit','2008-08-14 18:42:56',0),(1140,'FEATURE_REV_DIGIT_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:56',0),(1141,'FEATURE_REV_DIGIT_LONG','US','\"Live Effects is the standout illustration feature. This will let you edit an object (including vector drawings), even after you have applied an effect to it. DTP tasks are made easier by new support for multiple page documents and an enhanced text tool.(tools) such as the colour picker - are one-click simplicity. The Transparency tool in particular is fast and easy to use.\"','2008-08-14 18:42:56',0),(1142,'FEATURE_REV_DIGIT_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:56',0),(1143,'FEATURE_REV_PC_PRO_2_NAME','US','PC Pro','2008-08-14 18:42:50',0),(1144,'FEATURE_REV_PC_PRO_2_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:50',0),(1145,'FEATURE_REV_PC_PRO_2_LONG','US','\"The program\'s main strength remains its underlying speed. Xara has always stood out for the astonishing speed of its vector handling, as well as the sheer hands-on creativity this enables. ..the ability to apply a drop shadow, graduated transparency, or both, to your text in real-time is impressive...You\'re getting an extraordinarily powerful package for little more than the upgrade cost of the latest Illustrator.\"','2008-08-14 18:42:50',0),(2666,'IMG_PCADVISOR_GOLD_JPG_URL','US','/files/img/us/pcadvisor_gold.jpg','2008-07-04 16:58:27',0),(1146,'FEATURE_REV_PC_PRO_2_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:50',0),(1147,'FEATURE_REV_PRACTICAL_WEB_DESIGN_NAME','US','Practical Web Design','2008-08-14 18:42:14',0),(1148,'FEATURE_REV_PRACTICAL_WEB_DESIGN_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:14',0),(1149,'FEATURE_REV_PRACTICAL_WEB_DESIGN_LONG','US','\"Although it\'s primarily known as a vector-drawing program, Xara Xtreme has capabilities that extend into photo-editing and animation, making it a great all-round tool for the creation of web graphics. Optimised for quick learning and rapid workflow, this is a deceptively powerful package.\"<br />\r\n<br />\"Importantly, Xara seems committed to maintaining its software\'s innovative edge.\"','2008-08-14 18:42:14',0),(1150,'FEATURE_REV_PRACTICAL_WEB_DESIGN_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:42:14',0),(1151,'FEATURE_REV_CHICAGO_TRIBUNE_NAME','US','Chicago Tribune','2008-08-14 18:43:50',0),(1152,'FEATURE_REV_CHICAGO_TRIBUNE_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:50',0),(1153,'FEATURE_REV_CHICAGO_TRIBUNE_LONG','US','\"This software draws on all the powers of a modern PC to give even beginners the ability to enhance our surroundings with home-brewed works of professional looking art.\"','2008-08-14 18:43:50',0),(1154,'FEATURE_REV_CHICAGO_TRIBUNE_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:50',0),(1155,'FEATURE_REV_LOS_ANGELES_TIMES_NAME','US','Los Angeles Times','2008-08-14 18:43:26',0),(1156,'FEATURE_REV_LOS_ANGELES_TIMES_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:26',0),(1157,'FEATURE_REV_LOS_ANGELES_TIMES_LONG','US','\"...the greatest thing about Xara Xtreme is the enjoyment one gets from just playing. It is the adult equivalent of that first tray of watercolors that enraptures children during art time in kingergarten.\"','2008-08-14 18:43:26',0),(1158,'FEATURE_REV_LOS_ANGELES_TIMES_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:26',0),(1159,'FEATURE_REV__NET_NAME','US','.net','2008-08-14 18:43:56',0),(1160,'FEATURE_REV__NET_SHORT','US','99%','2008-08-14 18:43:56',0),(1161,'FEATURE_REV__NET_LONG','US','\"This graphics package is a good budget buy, but that\'s just the beginning.\"','2008-08-14 18:43:56',0),(1162,'FEATURE_REV__NET_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:56',0),(1163,'AWARD_DOTNET','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/dotnet.gif\" />','2008-03-13 14:59:29',0),(1164,'AWARD_DESIGNERTODAY','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/designertoday.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:00:01',0),(1165,'AWARD_PCPRO_RECOMMENDED','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/pcpro_recommended.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:00:35',0),(1166,'AWARD_PCW_RECOMMENDED','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/pcw_recommended.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:01:01',0),(1167,'AWARD_COMPUTERARTS_RECOMMENDED','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/computerarts_recommended.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:01:46',0),(1168,'AWARD_COMPUTERSHOPPER_BESTBUY','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/computershopper_bestbuy.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:02:20',0),(1169,'AWARD_ABOUTCOM','US','<img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/us/awards/aboutcom.gif\" />','2008-03-13 15:02:40',0),(1170,'FEATURE_REV_DESIGNER_TODAY1_NAME','US','Designer Today','2008-08-14 18:45:30',0),(1171,'FEATURE_REV_DESIGNER_TODAY1_SHORT','US','Editor\'s Choice / Best Product','2008-08-14 18:45:30',0),(1172,'FEATURE_REV_DESIGNER_TODAY1_LONG','US','\"No matter who you are and what you use now for your graphics and drawing, you should give Xara Xtreme a try.\"<br />\r\n<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.designertoday.com/tabindex-13/tabid-104/itemid-2736/DesktopDefault.aspx\">Read the review</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.designertoday.com/tabindex-13/tabid-104/itemid-2736/DesktopDefault.aspx\"></a>','2008-08-14 18:45:30',0),(1173,'FEATURE_REV_DESIGNER_TODAY1_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:45:30',0),(1174,'FEATURE_REV_PCW_NAME','US','PCW','2008-08-14 18:44:58',0),(1175,'FEATURE_REV_PCW_SHORT','US','4 stars - Recommended','2008-08-14 18:44:58',0),(1176,'FEATURE_REV_PCW_LONG','US','\"Xara Xtreme provides just about everything you\'ll need for creating and editing graphics, whether bitmap or vector.\"<br />\r\n<br />\"A powerful graphics and photo editing tool that\'s easy to get to grips with.\"','2008-08-14 18:44:58',0),(1177,'FEATURE_REV_PCW_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:44:58',0),(1257,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_ARTS_2_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:43:20',0),(1178,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_SHOPPER_NAME','US','Computer Shopper','2008-08-14 18:45:24',0),(1179,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_SHOPPER_SHORT','US','5 stars - Best Buy','2008-08-14 18:45:24',0),(1180,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_SHOPPER_LONG','US','\"At this price, Xara Xtreme is almost an obligatory buy even for users with only a passing interest in drawing software.\"<br />\r\n<br />&quot;Compared with rivals the program is amazingly responsive and it actually takes a few minutes to get used to the fact that you don\'t have to wait after you make a change or finish dragging an object around.&quot;<br />\r\n<br />&quot;Rewarding to use and fantastic value.&quot;<br />\r\n<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.pcpro.co.uk/shopper/labs/78965/xara-xtreme.html\">Read the review</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.pcpro.co.uk/shopper/labs/78965/xara-xtreme.html\"></a>','2008-08-14 18:45:24',0),(1181,'FEATURE_REV_COMPUTER_SHOPPER_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:45:24',0),(1182,'FEATURE_REV_ABOUT_COM_NAME','US','About.com','2008-08-14 18:45:57',0),(1183,'FEATURE_REV_ABOUT_COM_SHORT','US','Guide\'s Choice','2008-08-14 18:45:57',0),(1184,'FEATURE_REV_ABOUT_COM_LONG','US','\"It may not be one of the \'big three\' drawing programs but it beats them in features, price and performance.\"<br />\r\n<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://graphicssoft.about.com/od/vectorbased/gr/xaraxtreme.htm\">Read the review</a><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://graphicssoft.about.com/od/vectorbased/gr/xaraxtreme.htm\"></a>','2008-08-14 18:45:57',0),(1185,'FEATURE_REV_ABOUT_COM_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-14 18:45:57',0),(2756,'EDUCATION_INTRO','US','<p>Xara software is a popular choice in education because of its unique combination of intuitive ease of use with powerful \'real world\' functionality. Our software is used in real commercial environments, but it is recognised for its accessibility to newcomers and short learning curve. All products are shipped with introductory movie tutorials and example graphics so you can see results in minutes, not hours! <br>\r\n<br>Xara titles are great value for money, but we offer further generous discounts to&nbsp;academic sites of any sort, including teachers and pupils,&nbsp;on all our graphics products – Xara Xtreme, Xara Web Designer, Xara3D, and Xara Menu Maker. <br>\r\n<br>Xara operates a simple-to-understand, quantity-based discount-structure, shown below (VAT will be added at 17.5% on orders in the EU). To take advantage of these discounts, simply purchase from one of our worldwide <a href=\"/ordering/education_resellers.asp\"><strong>academic resellers</strong></a>. Educational sites <strong>in the UK</strong> also have the option to order directly from our office in England (contact details below) and purchase orders are accepted.','2010-01-01 21:53:40',0),(1190,'FEATURE_TEST_STEVE_DORIF_NAME','US','Steve Dorif','2009-08-05 18:00:24',0),(1191,'FEATURE_TEST_STEVE_DORIF_SHORT','US','I am vastly impressed with Xtreme, it is an outstanding piece of software and a joy to use.','2009-08-05 18:00:24',0),(1192,'FEATURE_TEST_STEVE_DORIF_LONG','US','\"I am vastly impressed with Xtreme, it is an outstanding piece of software and a joy to use. <br>\r\n<br>Having seen some of the \'paintings\' created with Xtreme, I thought that I would try it out myself and I found there are some distinct advantages in painting with Xtreme, ease of use, total control and the shear playful attitude towards solving illustration problems it fills a user with.\"','2009-08-05 18:00:24',0),(4952,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WN5_CAT1','US','','2009-05-21 19:12:09',1),(4953,'FEATURE_CAT_WN5_CAT2','US','Other Enhancements','2009-05-21 19:12:15',1),(4954,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WN5_CAT2','US','','2009-05-21 19:12:15',1),(4955,'FEATURE_CAT_WN5_CAT3','US','Other minor improvements','2009-05-21 15:05:43',1),(1193,'FEATURE_TEST_STEVE_DORIF_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-05 18:00:24',0),(1194,'FEATURE_TEST_DAVE_WILKINSON_NAME','US','Dave Wilkinson','2008-08-12 11:12:52',0),(1195,'FEATURE_TEST_DAVE_WILKINSON_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:12:52',0),(1196,'FEATURE_TEST_DAVE_WILKINSON_LONG','US','\"Thanks for ... all the work you have put into Xtreme Pro. The pdf import/export is fantastic - I can work exclusively in Xara but still provide my customers with .ai and .eps (although, of course I do my best to persuade them that they just need pdf!).\"','2009-05-19 13:19:51',0),(1210,'FEATURE_TEST_DEREK_COOPER_NAME','US','Derek Cooper','2008-08-12 11:11:20',0),(1211,'FEATURE_TEST_DEREK_COOPER_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:11:20',0),(1212,'FEATURE_TEST_DEREK_COOPER_LONG','US','\"I\'ve used Xara since Xara Studio and it\'s grown with me as an essential part of my P.C. Toolbox to the point now where it is virtually the only tool in the box. I\'ve tried other pieces of software from time to time though the comparison with Xara has always left them wanting in some respect or another and they have eventually been discarded. Please keep up the good work. At 55 years old I\'ve never written a fan letter before. \"','2009-05-19 13:20:08',0),(1197,'FEATURE_TEST_DAVE_WILKINSON_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:12:52',0),(1198,'FEATURE_TEST_LORRAINE_BACKEY_NAME','US','Lorraine Backey','2008-08-12 11:12:30',0),(1199,'FEATURE_TEST_LORRAINE_BACKEY_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:12:30',0),(1200,'FEATURE_TEST_LORRAINE_BACKEY_LONG','US','\"I am very enthusiastic about Xara Xtreme. I am not all that computer savvy (I\'m 81 and they didn\'t have PCs when I worked) but when I saw Xara demonstrated, I knew I had to have it. It is a terrific program and while I am not all that proficient with it, I am enjoying learning it.\"','2009-05-19 13:22:20',0),(4963,'FEATURE_WN5_ANCHORED_GRAPHICS_LONG','US','<p>&nbsp;Some more content</p>','2009-05-20 20:27:56',1),(1206,'FEATURE_TEST_BRIAN_CHAPMAN_NAME','US','Brian Chapman','2008-08-12 11:11:42',0),(1207,'FEATURE_TEST_BRIAN_CHAPMAN_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:11:42',0),(1208,'FEATURE_TEST_BRIAN_CHAPMAN_LONG','US','\"I\'ve used Xara for over six years now. Its advantages over other graphic software I\'ve used has allowed me to generate the technical graphics I need to \"impress the boss\" and meet or even exceed my deadlines. Thanks Xara...you\'ve made <strong>the best program ever!</strong> \"','2009-05-19 13:17:15',0),(4974,'FEATURE_CONTENT-AWARE_RESCALING_SHORT','US','Intelligent image scaling technology that allows images to be stretched or squashed while retaining the proportions of important parts of the picture.','2009-06-04 18:08:40',1),(1209,'FEATURE_TEST_BRIAN_CHAPMAN_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:11:42',0),(1201,'FEATURE_TEST_LORRAINE_BACKEY_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:12:30',0),(1202,'FEATURE_TEST_CARL_HUBERT_NAME','US','Carl Hubert','2009-08-06 12:11:04',0),(1203,'FEATURE_TEST_CARL_HUBERT_SHORT','US','It is a fantastic program to add for any Graphic Artist. Easy to learn with the best teaching tools I have ever seen in a graphics package.','2009-08-06 12:11:04',0),(1204,'FEATURE_TEST_CARL_HUBERT_LONG','US','\"It is a fantastic program to add for any Graphic Artist. <strong>Easy to learn with the best teaching tools I have ever seen</strong> in a graphics package.....I should know, as I have them all including Adobe\'s CS2 Premium and CorelDRAW CS 12. \"','2009-08-06 12:11:04',0),(4972,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_KEYWORDS','US','object gallery;','2009-06-04 17:53:07',1),(4973,'FEATURE_CONTENT-AWARE_RESCALING_NAME','US','Content-Aware Rescaling','2009-06-04 18:08:40',1),(1218,'FEATURE_TEST_RICHARD_BAMSEY_NAME','US','Richard Bamsey','2008-08-12 11:10:36',0),(1213,'FEATURE_TEST_DEREK_COOPER_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:11:20',0),(1214,'FEATURE_TEST_SAM_WHITE_NAME','US','Sam White','2009-08-06 12:12:29',0),(1215,'FEATURE_TEST_SAM_WHITE_SHORT','US','I just wanted to say is WOW do you overdeliver! You\'ve done it again and given us far more on the CD than I would have ever expected.','2009-08-06 12:12:29',0),(1216,'FEATURE_TEST_SAM_WHITE_LONG','US','\"I just wanted to say is <strong>WOW do you overdeliver</strong>! You\'ve done it again and given us far more on the CD than I would have ever expected. Thank you so much for over-delivering again on another great Xara product. Great job Xara crew. \"','2009-08-06 12:12:29',0),(4956,'FEATURE_CAT_DESC_WN5_CAT3','US','','2009-05-21 15:05:43',1),(4957,'FEATURE_WN5_CONTENT-AWARE_SCALING_NAME','US','Content-Aware Scaling','2009-05-21 18:09:09',1),(4958,'FEATURE_WN5_CONTENT-AWARE_SCALING_SHORT','US','Content-Aware Scaling','2009-05-21 18:09:09',1),(4959,'FEATURE_WN5_CONTENT-AWARE_SCALING_LONG','US','<p>The Photo Tool has been enhanced with a new intelligent image scaling technology that allows images to be stretched or squashed while retaining the proportions of important parts of the picture.</p>\r\n<p>This can provide a near miraculous ability to stretch and change the aspect ratio of photos, without apparently distorting the content of the photo.</p>','2009-05-21 18:09:09',1),(1205,'FEATURE_TEST_CARL_HUBERT_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-06 12:11:04',0),(1217,'FEATURE_TEST_SAM_WHITE_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-06 12:12:29',0),(1219,'FEATURE_TEST_RICHARD_BAMSEY_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:10:36',0),(1220,'FEATURE_TEST_RICHARD_BAMSEY_LONG','US','<strong>&quot;</strong>I just wanted to say what an <strong>excellent product</strong> Xara X is. I have been using Xara since the very first beta version was shown at Newbury years ago and <strong>I have never found anything to touch it</strong>.<strong>&quot;</strong><br />\r\n<br /><strong>&quot;</strong>I have tried all the rest and some of them are probably still loaded on my system, they just don\'t get used. <strong>&quot;</strong>','2008-08-12 11:10:36',0),(1258,'OTHER_XARA_PRODUCTS','US','Other Xara Products...','2008-03-17 18:21:41',1),(1259,'OTHER_XARA_PRODUCTS_DESC','US','Looking for our other products?  Click the logos below to view all other product information.','2008-03-17 18:23:36',1),(1221,'FEATURE_TEST_RICHARD_BAMSEY_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:10:36',0),(1222,'FEATURE_TEST_DAN__NAME','US','Dan ','2009-08-06 12:13:56',0),(1223,'FEATURE_TEST_DAN__SHORT','US','I\'ve been a designer for 10 years and a user of CorelXARA since ver 1.0. What a great product! I am confused as to why this is not the most popular graphics tool on the market. ','2009-08-06 12:13:56',0),(1224,'FEATURE_TEST_DAN__LONG','US','\"I\'ve been a designer for 10 years and a user of CorelXARA since ver 1.0. <strong>What a great product</strong>!!!&quot; <br>\r\n<br>\"I am confused as to why this is not the most popular graphics tool on the market. \"','2009-08-06 12:13:56',0),(1225,'FEATURE_TEST_DAN__KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-06 12:13:56',0),(1226,'FEATURE_TEST_LADISLAV_SEREDI_NAME','US','Ladislav Seredi','2009-08-06 12:14:34',0),(1227,'FEATURE_TEST_LADISLAV_SEREDI_SHORT','US','Congratulations! Your developers did a truly brilliant job.','2009-08-06 12:14:34',0),(1228,'FEATURE_TEST_LADISLAV_SEREDI_LONG','US','\"Congratulations!\" <br>\r\n<br>&quot;I belive that the new Xara X offers <strong>the best price-performance ratio on the web graphics market</strong> and leaves the competition far behind.&quot; <br>\r\n<br>&quot;Your developers did a truly <strong>brilliant</strong> job. \"','2009-08-06 12:14:34',0),(4964,'FEATURE_WN5_ANCHORED_GRAPHICS_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-05-20 20:27:56',1),(4965,'FEATURE_WN5_TRANSPARENCY_TOOL_NAME','US','The Transparency Tool now supports multi-stage graduated transparencies (works rather like multi-stage graduated color fills).','2009-05-21 17:47:50',1),(4966,'FEATURE_WN5_TRANSPARENCY_TOOL_SHORT','US','The Transparency Tool now supports multi-stage graduated transparencies (works rather like multi-stage graduated color fills).','2009-05-21 17:47:50',1),(4967,'FEATURE_WN5_TRANSPARENCY_TOOL_LONG','US','','2009-05-21 17:47:50',1),(1229,'FEATURE_TEST_LADISLAV_SEREDI_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-08-06 12:14:34',0),(1230,'FEATURE_TEST_ROL-_MAARSCHALKERWEERD_NAME','US','Roland Maarschalkerweerd','2008-08-12 11:00:26',0),(1231,'FEATURE_TEST_ROL-_MAARSCHALKERWEERD_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 11:00:26',0),(1232,'FEATURE_TEST_ROL-_MAARSCHALKERWEERD_LONG','US','\"Right after your mail I downloaded the Bèta-Version and I want to say: <strong>\'GREAT program\'</strong>.&quot; <br>\r\n<br>&quot;Although Fireworks and Xara X are not the same, they are comparable and leave only <strong>one definite winner; Xara X</strong>. What more can a professional, semi-professional or just-for-fun-professional want? \"','2009-05-19 13:23:07',0),(4960,'FEATURE_WN5_CONTENT-AWARE_SCALING_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-05-21 18:09:09',1),(4961,'FEATURE_WN5_ANCHORED_GRAPHICS_NAME','US','Anchored Graphics','2009-05-20 20:27:56',1),(4962,'FEATURE_WN5_ANCHORED_GRAPHICS_SHORT','US','Anchored Graphics','2009-05-20 20:27:56',1),(1233,'FEATURE_TEST_ROL-_MAARSCHALKERWEERD_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 11:00:26',0),(1234,'FEATURE_TEST_DANIEL_WILL-HARRIS_NAME','US','Daniel Will-Harris','2008-08-12 10:59:46',0),(1235,'FEATURE_TEST_DANIEL_WILL-HARRIS_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 10:59:46',0),(1236,'FEATURE_TEST_DANIEL_WILL-HARRIS_LONG','US','\" I\'ve used every major graphics program on the market - and the program I use every day for my own web and print design work is Xara. It\'s fast, reliable, and more flexible than any other graphics program I\'ve used. It\'s real-time anti-aliasing means what you see is really what you get, and it\'s live transparency feature is still unmatched.\" <br>\r\n<br>&quot;Xara X\'s new features are all <strong>beautifully designed</strong> so that you see your changes in real time. The new bevel and shadow features let you add depth to flat vector graphics and the advanced export options give you even more control.&quot; <br>\r\n<br>\"Xara is the best. Period. \"','2009-05-19 13:19:02',0),(4969,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_NAME','US','Object Gallery','2009-06-04 17:53:07',1),(4970,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_SHORT','US','A powerful and flexible tool for viewing, re-ordering, hiding and locking layers and pages in your document.','2009-06-04 17:53:07',1),(4971,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_LONG','US','<p>The Object Gallery is a&nbsp;powerful and flexible tool for viewing, re-ordering, hiding and locking&nbsp;layers and pages in your document.</p>\r\n<p>Everything in your document is presented in a heirarchical, expandable list - at the top level are the pages, and inside each page are the named layers of the document.</p>','2009-06-04 17:53:07',1),(1237,'FEATURE_TEST_DANIEL_WILL-HARRIS_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 10:59:46',0),(1238,'FEATURE_TEST_GARY_W__PRIESTER_NAME','US','Gary W. Priester','2008-08-12 10:59:24',0),(1239,'FEATURE_TEST_GARY_W__PRIESTER_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 10:59:24',0),(1240,'FEATURE_TEST_GARY_W__PRIESTER_LONG','US','\" If I could only take one drawing application to that fabled desert isle, it would be Xara X. It\'s <strong>efficient</strong>, it\'s <strong>incredibly fast</strong>, and it\'s <strong>considerate</strong>...&quot; <br>\r\n<br>&quot;Xara 2 was a <strong>breakthrough product</strong> in terms of speed and ease of use. <strong>Xara X raises the bar to new heights</strong> with all the features you need to create exciting illustrations and striking Web images and animations. \"','2009-05-19 13:21:09',0),(5061,'WHATSNEW_PREVIOUS','US','If you own a version that pre-dates Xara Xtreme 4, then you may also be interested in what\'s new since these versions.','2009-05-21 13:59:28',1),(4968,'FEATURE_WN5_TRANSPARENCY_TOOL_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-05-21 17:47:50',1),(1241,'FEATURE_TEST_GARY_W__PRIESTER_KEYWORDS','US','','2008-08-12 10:59:24',0),(1242,'FEATURE_TEST_ALEX_POLSKY_NAME','US','Alex Polsky','2008-08-12 10:59:04',0),(1243,'FEATURE_TEST_ALEX_POLSKY_SHORT','US','','2008-08-12 10:59:04',0),(1244,'FEATURE_TEST_ALEX_POLSKY_LONG','US','\" [CorelXARA] remains an example of great sortware... slim, intuitive and smart. I\'ve got Fireworks from Macromedia, and <strong>there\'s no comparison</strong>... Xara is so much more straightforward. \"','2009-05-19 13:16:47',0),(4975,'FEATURE_CONTENT-AWARE_RESCALING_LONG','US','<p>The Photo Tool has been enhanced with a new intelligent image scaling technology that allows images to be stretched or squashed while retaining the proportions of important parts of the picture.</p>\r\n<p>This can provide a near miraculous ability to stretch and change the aspect ratio of photos, without apparently distorting the content of the photo.</p>\r\n<p>Take this example of a photo of the famous Torii Gate in Japan. The first photo is the original, clearly the gate itself is the main subject of this picture. The second photo has been stretched in the normal way with the Selector tool. Even with moderate stretching it\'s obvious the proportions of the gate have been badly distorted.&nbsp; In the third photo we\'ve using Content Aware Scaling -&nbsp;and now&nbsp;the gate proportions are in tact even at this extreme stretch, which is twice as wide as the original.</p>','2009-06-04 18:08:40',1),(4976,'FEATURE_CONTENT-AWARE_RESCALING_KEYWORDS','US','content aware scaling;','2009-06-04 18:08:40',1),(4977,'FEATURE_SPELL_CHECK_NAME','U