;Euro</a>','2009-04-15 10:11:18',0),(2738,'FEATURE_REV_SOFTWARE_COM_SHORT','US','','2008-08-14 18:46:40',1),(2739,'FEATURE_REV_SOFTWARE_COM_LONG','US','“Xara Xtreme has the world\'s most sophisticated, highest performance vector rendering engine. For the user this speed means less wait, and a more satisfying working environment. It also means more productivity and the ability to create more complex drawings, in less time.”<br />\r\n<p>&quot;With Xara Xtreme, when you create an image it appears instantly on the screen.&quot;</p>\r\n<p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.software.com/view/9540/25/xara-xtreme-4\">Read the Review</a></p>','2008-08-14 18:46:40',1),(2317,'LANGUAGELIST','FR','<a href=\"/us/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_us.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;États-Unis</a><a href=\"/uk/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_uk.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Royaume-Uni</a><a href=\"/de/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_de.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Allemagne</a><a href=\"/es/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_es.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Espagne</a><a href=\"/eu/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"/img/global/flag_eu.png\">&nbsp;Euro</a>','2009-04-15 10:13:01',0),(2318,'LANGUAGELIST','ES','<a href=\"/us/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_us.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Estados&nbsp;Unidos</a><a href=\"/uk/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_uk.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Reino&nbsp;Unido</a><a href=\"/de/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_de.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Alemania</a><a href=\"/fr/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/img/global/flag_fr.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" />&nbsp;Francia</a><a href=\"/eu/setlanguage\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align: middle\" src=\"/img/gl