illustration software, Xara Studio, was licensed to Corel and distributed for many years as CorelXARA. Now back under Xara control this product has been enhanced and relaunched as Xara Xtreme.<br>\r\n<br>Xara is headquartered in the historic house, Gaddesden Place, in the UK, north of London.<br>\r\n<br>In January 2007 Xara was acquired by <a title=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.magix.com/\">MAGIX AG</a>, and now operates as a wholly owned subsidiary.','2009-01-06 10:23:21',1),(2995,'PAGE_TITLE_AL__ABOUT','US','About Xara','2008-09-02 17:59:14',1),(2996,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__ABOUT','US','','2008-09-02 17:59:14',1),(2997,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__ABOUT','US','','2008-09-02 17:59:14',1),(2998,'MENU_JOBS','US','Jobs','2008-09-02 18:01:24',1),(2999,'MENU_LOCATION_MAP','US','Location Map','2008-09-02 18:01:57',1),(3000,'FEATURE_REV_IMAGINEFX__SHORT','DE','...','2008-09-02 21:24:51',1),(3001,'FEATURE_REV_IMAGINEFX__LONG','DE','...','2008-09-02 21:24:51',1),(3002,'MXPGD1','DE','MAGIX Xtreme Foto &amp; Grafik Designer 1','2008-09-02 21:26:25',1),(3003,'MXPGD2','DE','MAGIX Xtreme Foto &amp; Grafik Designer 5','2009-07-09 10:05:36',1),(3004,'COMPANY_FOOTER','DE','<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<hr /><br />\r\nRegistered in England and Wales: Company registration number 3097032: Registered Office: Clifton House, Bunnian Place, Basingstoke, RG21 7JE: Company HQ: Gaddesden Place, Hemel Hempstead, HP2 6EX: VAT registration number 814038749','2008-09-02 21:27:10',1),(3005,'PAGE_TITLE_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_PLUGINS','DE','Zu Xara Xtreme kompatible Plug-ins','2008-09-03 10:01:35',1),(3006,'PAGE_KEYWORDS_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_PLUGINS','DE','plugins, plug-ins, photoshop plug-ins','2008-09-03 10:01:35',1),(3007,'PAGE_DESCRIPTION_AL__PRODUCTS_XTREME_PLUGINS','DE','Zu Xara Xtreme kompatible Plug-ins','2008-09-03 10:01:35',1),(3008,'OTHER_COMPETITOR','DE','Andere Anbieter','2008-09-03 10:01:35',1),(3009,'UPGRADING_FROM','DE','Upgrade von','2008-09-03 10:01:35',1),(3010,'UPGRADING_TO','DE','Upgrade zu'