plates','2009-07-06 17:52:59',0),(4441,'FEATURE_PROFESSIONAL_TEMPLATES_WD_SHORT','US','Web Designer also includes template designs for individual graphics, from headings and buttons to text boxes and speech bubbles! Again they are all created by professional designers and can be customized to fit your site in seconds. \r\nThese individual graphics can be exported in the standard web formats such as GIF, JPEG, PNG for use on existing websites, or they can be added to any page being created in Web Designer.','2009-07-06 17:52:59',0),(4442,'FEATURE_PROFESSIONAL_TEMPLATES_WD_LONG','US','','2009-07-06 17:52:59',0),(4443,'FEATURE_PROFESSIONAL_TEMPLATES_WD_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-07-06 17:52:59',0),(4444,'FEATURE_CREATE_CUSTOM_GRAPHICS_WD_NAME','US','Or create custom graphics','2009-07-06 17:52:53',0),(4445,'FEATURE_CREATE_CUSTOM_GRAPHICS_WD_SHORT','US','If you don\'t find a template to fit the bill, no problem, Web Designer includes comprehensive, intuitive and powerful drawing tools from our award winning illustration software Xara Xtreme. \r\nSo you can create your own graphics from scratch and either add them to the page being created in Web Designer or export them as JPEG, PNGs or GIFs.','2009-07-06 17:52:53',0),(4446,'FEATURE_CREATE_CUSTOM_GRAPHICS_WD_LONG','US','','2009-07-06 17:52:53',0),(4447,'FEATURE_CREATE_CUSTOM_GRAPHICS_WD_KEYWORDS','US','','2009-07-06 17:52:53',0),(4448,'FEATURE_TOTAL_DESIGN_FREEDOM_WD_NAME','US','Total design freedom','2009-07-06 17:53:04',0),(4449,'FEATURE_TOTAL_DESIGN_FREEDOM_WD_SHORT','US','Web Designer gives you total design freedom - using drag and drop you can literally place anything, anywhere on the page. And things which are normally difficult to achieve in HTML are a snap in Web Designer - for example text with curved edges, text or graphics at an angle, text flowing around objects - no problem!','2009-07-06 17:53:04',0),(4450,'FEATURE_TOTAL_DESIGN_FREEDOM_WD_LONG','US','','2009-07-06 17:53:04',0),(4451,'FEATURE_TOTAL_DESIGN_FREEDO