your site through this link (paid quarterly, personal commission payments subject to a minimum). <br>\r\n<br>If that sounds like a good idea, then read through the Terms &amp; Conditions in the affiliate dialog and then simply select one of the options at the bottom:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Please credit my Xara account with any commission. I have read, understood and accept the affiliate terms and conditions above. </li>\r\n<li>Please donate any commission earned through links from my site to charity. I have read, understood and accept the affiliate terms and conditions above. </li></ul>\r\n<p>Your ‘Made with Xara’ link is then automatically updated to include your affiliate URL. If you select Option 2 you will be offered a choice of Featured Charities to choose from (see below). These will change from time to time, we will notify you by email of any changes. <br>\r\n<br>If you pass for now but decide you’d like to join later, or if you wish to change from the personal to the charity option or vice versa, then you can return to the Affiliate dialog by selecting the Affiliate option in the Help menu of Xara Xtreme and Web Designer. <br>\r\n<br><strong>If you are already a Xara affiliate:</strong><br>\r\nPlease still select one of the two options so we know whether to add the commission to your account or pay it to the charity. If you choose the former then the commission payments will appear in your normal affiliate commission report alongside your other products. If you choose charity then the stats will not show in your report.\r\n<p><strong>Featured Charities:</strong><br>\r\nIf you choose to have your commission paid to a charity, you will be able to select a charity of your choice from our Featured Charities. These will change from time to time, we will notify affiliates of any changes by email. These are our current Featured Charities<strong>:</strong>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.msf.org/\"><strong>Medecins Sans Frontieres</strong><br>\r\n</a>MSF is an independent humanitarian aid agency committed to providing medical aid wherever it is most needed, regardless of race, religion, politics or sex, and raising awareness of the plight of the people they help.&nbsp;\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.soschildren.org/\"><strong>SOS Children</strong><br>\r\n</a>SOS Children provides family homes for children who have no one else to care for them, currently some 60,000 orphaned or abandoned children in 123 countries around the world.\r\n<p><strong><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.foei.org/\">Friends Of The Earth International</a></strong> <br>\r\nThe world\'s largest grassroots environmental network. Friends of the Earth inspires solutions to environmental problems which make life better for people, by working towards a world where resources are used sustainably and fairly.\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.shelterbox.org/\"><strong>Shelter Box</strong><br>\r\n</a>Shelter Box&nbsp;provide&nbsp;emergency&nbsp;shelter to people displaced by natural and other disasters.\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.rotary.org/en/EndPolio/Pages/learn.aspx\"><strong>Rotary Polio Plus</strong><br>\r\n</a>A partnership between Rotary International, Governments and NGOs across the world to completely eradicate polio. Rotary\'s current challenge is to <a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.rotary.org/en/MediaAndNews/News/Pages/090121_news_gates255milliongrant2009ia.aspx\">raise $100M</a> to match&nbsp;a grant from the The Bill &amp; Melinda Gates Foundation.&nbsp;\r\n<p>Where donations have to be made to national offices, the payment will be made to the UK office.</p>','2009-09-08 10:39:49',1),(4607,'FLV_WEBDESIGNER_INTRO_V2_FLV','US','<div id=\"FLV_WEBDESIGNER_INTRO_V2_FLV\" style=\"border:1px #797979 solid; width:380px; height:260px;\">Please install Flash&reg; and turn on Javascript.</div>\n			<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n			// <![CDATA[\n			var so = new SWFObject(\"/lib/mediaplayer.swf\",\"FLV_WEBDESIGNER_INTRO_V2_FLV\",\"380\",\"260\"