009-06-02 16:01:40',1),(5173,'COMMUNITY_TITLE','US','Community','2009-06-02 16:04:56',1),(5174,'COMMUNITY_PAGE','US','<p>The Xara community is one of the great strengths of Xara products, providing independent support, inspiration and encouragement to users of all Xara products. Here are some of the best resources available.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.talkgraphics.com/\">TalkGraphics Forums</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>Popular, active and welcoming&nbsp;independent forums moderated by volunteers from the Xara community, with forums for each of the Xara products plus a wide range of graphics related topics. With more than 19,000 members and over 300,000 posts there\'s something for everyone with an interest in graphics.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.xaraxone.com/\">The Xara Xone</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>More then 10 years of invaluable Xara material created by Xara guru Gary Priester including tutorials, tips, Xara shareware, Featured Artists and more. Updated every month.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xara Art</strong></p>\r\n<p>There\'s plenty of Xara artwork on display on the web but here\'s&nbsp;three of the best: </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The <a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/gallery/\">Xara Gallery</a> on this website displays artwork sent in by our customers </li>\r\n<li>Don\'t miss the <a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.xaraxone.com/html/featured_art_2009.html\">Featured Artist</a> every month&nbsp; (since 1999!) at the Xara Xone&nbsp; </li>\r\n<li>Xara artists also put on a great show in the Gallery at <a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.graphics.com/modules.php?set_albumName=album06&amp;op=modload&amp;name=Gallery&amp;file=index&amp;include=view_album.php\">graphics.com</a> </li></ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong>YouTube</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Xara community are very active&nbsp;on <a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/results?search_type=&amp;search_query=xara&amp;aq=f\">YouTube</a> - you\'ll find plenty of movies featuring Xara products - inspirational, funny, instructive and eccentric in turn!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Of course Xara also provide support and news services for our community:</p>\r\n<p><strong>The Outsider</strong></p>\r\n<p>Our monthly newsletter packed with inspirational art created by Xara owners, tutorials, tips, contests and the latest news. You can find back issues and subscribe&nbsp;<a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/outsider/\">here</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xara News</strong></p>\r\n<p>Check in on our <a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/news/\">news page</a> for the latest Xara info.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Twitter</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you like your news hot off the press then this is the perfect option for you. <a title=\"\" href=\"http://twitter.com/xaragroup\">Sign up</a> as a Xara follower and receive our tweets about the most exciting new resources - movies, tutorials, art - and the latest news, as it happens.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The Affiliate Program</strong></p>\r\n<p>There are thousands of Xara affiliates - why not join them and help spread the word about Xara products, and earn some commission&nbsp;into the bargain&nbsp;- either for your own account or for charities. Find out more on our <a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/referrer/\">Affiliate page</a>.</p>','2009-06-03 15:21:46',1),(5175,'COMPANY_TITLE','US','Company','2009-06-02 16:05:44',1),(5176,'COMPANY_PAGE','US','<p>In addition to product information you can find the following resources on the Xara site.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.xara.com/about/\">About</a>&nbsp;An introduction to&nbsp;Xara Group Ltd</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/press/\">Press</a>&nbsp;Resources for the press and an index of press releases</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/news/\">News</a>&nbsp;The latest news from Xara</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/ordering/world.asp\">Resellers</a>&nbsp;A list of Xara\'s resellers worldwide</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://www.xara.com/contact/\">Contact</a>&nbsp;How to contact the different departments at Xara</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"\" href=\"http://site.xara.com/support/logos/\">Logos &amp; Graphics</a>&nbsp;Resources for partners - affiliates, referrers and&nbsp;resellers</p>','2009-06-03 15:43:18',1),(5177,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_PRO_NAME','US','Object Gallery (Advanced)','2009-06-04 17:53:32',1),(5178,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_PRO_SHORT','US','The Pro Object Gallery is a powerful and flexible tool for viewing, re-ordering, hiding and locking not just layers, but everything from individual objects on the page to pages in your document.','2009-06-04 17:53:32',1),(5179,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_PRO_LONG','US','<p>The Object Gallery in Xtreme Pro is a&nbsp;powerful and flexible tool for viewing, re-ordering, hiding and locking not just layers, but everything from individual objects on the page to pages in your document.</p>\r\n<p>Everything in your document is presented in a heirarchical, expandable list.&nbsp;At the top level are the pages, and inside each page are the named layers of the document.&nbsp; In Xtreme Pro you can go to the next level which shows all&nbsp;the objects on the page. The Gallery provides thumbnail views of all objects.</p>\r\n<p>The Object Gallery makes it easy to find, select, lock or hide objects inside complex drawings, or objects inside groups or even hidden under other objects on the page.</p>','2009-06-04 17:53:32',1),(5180,'FEATURE_OBJECT_GALLERY_PRO_KEYWORDS','US','object gallery;','2009-06-04 17:53:32',1),(5183,'FEATURE_WN5_OBJECT_GALLERY_XTR_LONG','US','<p>The Object Gallery is a&nbsp;powerful and flexible tool for viewing, re-ordering, hiding and locking layers and&nbsp;pages in your document.</p>\r\n<p>Everything in your document is presented in a heirarchical, expandable list - at the top level are the pages, and inside each page are the named layers of the document.</p>\r\n<p>This is a new and intuitive way to manage layers, 