INSERT INTO `item_keyword` VALUES (1734,1,2,'field','html','intro',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'RSS (most commonly translated as \'Really Simple Syndication\' but sometimes \'Rich Site Summary\') is a family of web feed formats used to publish frequently updated works - such as blog entries, news headlines, audio, and video - in a standardized format. Below we give a step by step guide to inserting two of these - WebRSS and FeedBucket.'),(1780,1,21,'field','html','intro',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Xara Xtreme 5 and Web Designer allow you to add tracking codes to your website in order to collect data on your site visitors.  Individual tracking codes can be inserted per page of your website, or the same tracking code can be applied to all your pages in your website.\r\n\r\nSimply insert the tracking code in the \'Tracker code\' field from the Website tab of Web Properties, then each page in your site will be tracked.  Alternatively, insert the code in the \'Tracker code\' field from the page tab in order to track a particular page. \r\n\r\nThere are many services providing site analytics including Google Analytics, Get Clicky, GoStats, Nedstats and OneStat.  Some services are free, others provide restricted data for free accounts.  Additionally some services require a graphic or link to be inserted in your web pages (one example is Get Clicky). Other services such as Google Analytics do not insert any links or graphics in to your web pages. Below, we give a step by step guide to inserting Google Analytics and Get Clicky.'),(1675,1,3,'field','html','intro_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Webrss allows you to insert any RSS feed in to your own website.  Simply add the URL of a feed, customize the widget and insert the code provided in to Web Designer/Xara Xtreme.\r\n\r\nBelow we give a step by step guide to inserting a WebRSS Widget.'),(52,1,22,'field','html','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<a href=\"http://webrss.com/login.php\" target=\"_blank\">Sign in</a> to your WebRSS account or <a href=\"http://webrss.com/signup.php\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a> to create a new account.'),(3204,1,23,'field','image','screenshot',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"file\":\"13.png\",\"folder\":\"2009\\/11\\/6\\/uBS6ALHX\",\"size\":7899,\"type\":\"image\\/png\"}'),(3205,1,23,'field','string','screenshot_align','center',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2535,1,24,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Click on the link \'Manage Widgets\'. This will direct you to a page displaying your current feeds.'),(3208,1,25,'field','string','screenshot_align','center',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2536,1,26,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Customize the feed as required and click on the button \'Save and grab code\'.'),(3209,1,27,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'WebRSS provides the required code in a variety of formats. We recommend selecting JavaScript or iframes. Please set the width of the iframe to the required value if you are selecting the iframe option.'),(2589,1,28,'field','image','icon',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"file\":\"rectangle.png\",\"folder\":\"2009\\/9\\/28\\/wl09il0g\",\"size\":0.63,\"type\":\"image\\/png\"}'),(2588,1,28,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Using the Rectangle tool, insert a placeholder on your web page where you wish the WebRSS Widget to appear.'),(2539,1,30,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enable the radio button \'Replace with HTML code\' and paste (Ctrl +V) the code you copied in step 5.'),(2386,1,31,'field','comment','step_text',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Click on OK to apply the changes and close the dialog.'),(2671,1,33,'field','comment','intro',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'There are many websites available where users can upload and share their video clips.  The vast majority offer their services for free and allow you to embed the video clips in to your own website.  Some even allow you to create an entire playlist or a list of favorites, which you can embed directly from their website.  Below we 